:\r\n0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">45<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 15.75pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;color:#404040;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></b><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/200422016223407.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">主要成分：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">非离子表面活性剂、阴离子表面活性剂、椰子油衍生物、芦荟提取物、抗菌剂等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品特点：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">用途广泛<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>具备多种清洗功能，广泛用于各类家居洗涤，例如：清洗地板、墙壁、瓷砖、浴缸、玻璃、木制家具、塑料制品等家居用品，还可用于洗车、洗手等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">浓缩配方<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>稀释使用，经济实惠，效果更佳。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">环保配方<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>不含磷酸盐，其表面活性剂具良好生物分解性能，保护生态环境。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">天然品质<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>含椰子油衍生物和芦荟提取物，性质温和，不刺激皮肤。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">功效独特<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>采用世界流行的特效抗菌剂，可去除污染物，有益健康。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美品质<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>功效独特，使用安全，气味芬芳。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">适用范围及用量：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">清洁地板、墙壁、浴缸、瓷砖、塑料制品等家居用品：每<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>毫升（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2/3</span>瓶盖）清洁剂，洗涤后用清水洗净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">清洗玻璃、木制家具等家居用品：每<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>毫升（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1/3</span>瓶盖）清洁剂，洗涤后用清水洗净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">洗车：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">用<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>毫升（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1/3</span>瓶盖）清洁剂，洗涤后用清水洗净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">洗手：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">用稀释清洁剂清洗，然后用清水冲净。<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>可根据洗涤需要<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>适当调整稀释浓度。<span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:65.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.5;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">环保又省力<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:26.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  ----</span><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美芦荟多用途清洁剂<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">特点：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、用途广泛：具备多种清洗功能，广泛用于各类家居洗涤，如：清洗地板、墙壁、瓷砖、浴缸、玻璃、木制家具，塑料制品等家居用品，还可用于洗车、洗手等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、浓缩配方：<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>的浓缩配方，就是说：一份的清洁剂、配<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>份的水就可以起到很好的洗涤效果。因完美清洁剂是高浓缩产品，一般不直接使用，所以特别配套另一个产品<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>稀释宝配合使用，以把完美产品演释得更完美。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、环保配方：不含磷酸盐，其表面活性剂具良好生物分解性能，保护生态环境；市面上洗洁剂多为石油副产品之提取物，含磷酸盐，不易过水，易留残，含<span lang=\"EN-US\">ABS</span>毒物，伤害皮肤，令皮肤粗糙引致过敏，残留物易积聚肝脏，危害健康。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、天然品质：含椰子油衍生物和天然芦荟提取物、性质温和，呵护皮肤，不至于因浸水时间太长，而伤害皮肤，它的酸碱性很接近人体皮肤的酸碱度，而芦荟成份对于皮肤病有辅助治疗作用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、功效独特：消毒杀菌；既能清洁看得见的污秽，又能清除肉眼看不见的有害细菌，才是理想的洗涤用品。完美芦荟多用途清洁剂采用目前世界流行的特效广谱抗菌剂<span lang=\"EN-US\">DP&mdash;300</span>，可将多种细菌杀灭。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#003300;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、获得国家食品级卫生许可证：它是国内极少的几个产品之一，采用食品级原料生产，安全可靠，在洗洁蔬菜、水果后，立刻食用对身体都无害。且气味芬芳。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#003300;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">适用范围及用量：<span lang=\"EN-US\">①</span>清洁地板、墙壁、浴缸、瓷砖、塑料制品等家居用品<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>每<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>毫升<span lang=\"EN-US\">(2</span>／<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>瓶盖<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>清洁剂，洗涤后用清水洗净；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span>清洗玻璃、木制家具等家居用品<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>每<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>毫升<span lang=\"EN-US\">(1</span>／<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>瓶盖<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>清洁剂，洗涤后用清水洗净；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span>洗车<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>用<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>升水加<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>毫升<span lang=\"EN-US\">(1</span>／<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>瓶盖<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>清洁剂，洗涤后用清水洗净；<span lang=\"EN-US\">④</span>洗手<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>用稀释清洁剂清洗，然后用清水冲净！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/218_thumb_G_1370058722453.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/218_G_1370058722116.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/218_G_1370058722409.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '65', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1371007811', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
