p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">75<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/XIYIYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">芦荟超浓缩洗衣液配方，含特效酶制剂，结合多种具有去污作用的表面活性剂，使去污更彻底、更全面。高浓缩配方，溶解迅速，抗硬水，易洗，易漂，省时节水。中性，温和，清新芬芳，保护衣物，持久如新。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-bidi;color:#0000CC\">主要成分：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">水、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C14-16</span>烯烃磺酸钠、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C12-14</span>仲链烷醇聚醚<span lang=\"EN-US\">-9</span>、月桂醇硫酸酯<span lang=\"EN-US\">TEA</span>盐、十二烷基苯磺酸、乙氧基二甘醇、月桂醇聚醚硫酸酯钠、聚乙二醇<span lang=\"EN-US\">-12</span>、椰油酰胺<span lang=\"EN-US\">DEA</span>、氢氧化钠、三氯卡班、蛋白酶、联苯乙烯二苯基二磺酸二钠、库拉索芦荟（<span lang=\"EN-US\">ALOE BARBADENSIS</span>）叶汁粉、香精。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#0000CC\">产品特点：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#0000CC\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">超强洗净<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>含超强蛋白酶，独具分解作用，如汗渍、血渍、奶渍等，洗净效果极佳。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">除臭保健<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>含有安全杀菌剂和除臭因子，可除去衣物上的臭味。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">护色艳彩<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>含环保型特效增艳剂<span lang=\"EN-US\">T-CBSX</span>（即：联苯乙烯二苯基二磺酸二钠），使浅、白色织物或颜色鲜亮的衣物保持洁白艳丽。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">保护皮肤<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>温和配方，含有芦荟提取物，椰子油衍生物。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">环保配方<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>采用具有生物降解性的原材料，不含磷和无机助洗剂。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">浓缩配方<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>稀释使用，经济实惠。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">省水易洗<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>清洗容易，节约水资源。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">清新香味<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;</span>芬芳香料，让您的衣物散发自然清香。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-bidi;color:#0000CC\">适用范围及用量：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">、适合洗涤水洗织物，包括婴、幼儿衣物和尿布，以及床上用品、家居装饰布料等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">、适合机洗和手洗<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">机洗：低水位用量约<span lang=\"EN-US\">1/3</span>瓶盖中水位用量约<span lang=\"EN-US\">2/3</span>瓶盖、高水位用量约<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>瓶盖<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">手洗：根据不同需要加入适量洗衣液洗涤，再用清水冲洗干净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">、将洗衣液溶于水中之后，放入衣物洗涤，为达到最佳洗涤效果，建议将衣物浸泡<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>分钟后再进行洗涤，效果更佳。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">、若衣物较脏，可适当增加洗衣液用量，或用温水洗涤。对于局部特别脏的衣物，可先将洗衣液直接涂抹在污渍处洗涤后，再用一般方式洗涤。（由于本产品是高浓缩配方，对容易褪色的衣物建议先将洗衣液涂在衣物不显眼处，保留一段时间，再用水冲净，如不褪色，方可在污渍处用原液进行预洗。）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-bidi;color:#0000CC\">注意：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#0000CC\">如不慎入眼，请立即用大量清水冲洗。</span><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T2E7PyXohaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2wgxGXe8OXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T2Gj5SXbhbXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T2zM99XXlbXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2YWG8XeJbXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T2c9G1XgXbXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/726086364/T2Ycy6XhdbXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2psHAXkdaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/726086364/T2i6TFXn0XXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T22s2tXo8XXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2mpzfXgBbXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0000CC\">美好生活 衣衣不舍</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0000CC\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:91.35pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.5;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0000CC\">----</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0000CC\">完美芦荟超浓缩洗衣液</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0000CC\">使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:blue\">将洗衣液溶于水中之后，再放人衣物洗涤，为达到最佳洗涤效果，对于局部特别脏的衣物，可先将洗衣液直接涂抹在污渍处，作预洗处理，再用一般方式洗涤。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:blue\">用洗衣机洗<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">一大桶的衣物只需要一小瓶盖完美超浓缩洗衣液就可以起到洁净衣物的效果；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:blue\">用手洗<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">根据不同需要加入适量洗衣液洗涤，再用清水冲洗干净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red\">注意：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">洗衣液不慎入眼，请立即用大量清水冲洗。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red\">小贴士：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">我们的洗衣液是微酸性的，而市面上的洗衣粉是碱性，当我们初期使用的时候，我们的洗衣液会把残留在衣服中的碱综合出来，但洗过几次以后，就会充分地发挥它的功效，达到最佳效果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0000CC\">怎样挑选质优洗衣液：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:blue\">洗衣液是洗衣的最终发展趋势，是洗衣粉的升级替代产品。在欧美地区它已取代洗衣粉，洗衣液的最大突破是可以充分溶解不致浪费，目前已在大陆市场崭露头角，但洗衣粉仍唱主角。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:blue\">下面是洗衣液的</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:blue\">鉴别方法</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">，为对其知之不深的主妇提供购买参照：<span lang=\"EN-US\">①</span>外观质量上乘的产品</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:blue\">均匀粘稠，无肉眼可见杂质或分层</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">，次品有下浓上稀的分层；<span lang=\"EN-US\">②</span>色泽好的洗衣液</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:blue\">颜色稳定</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">，长期放置不变色，较差的会有色散、褪色现象；<span lang=\"EN-US\">③</span>溶解性能强，能</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:blue\">迅速溶解于水</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">，均匀作用于衣物的是质量过关的产品，难溶于水或需长时间搅拌，只起局部清洁效果的是质量不过关产品；<span lang=\"EN-US\">④</span>香味好的洗衣液</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:blue\">香味纯正、持久</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">，差的会偏酸，带点涩味；<span lang=\"EN-US\">⑤</span>家用效果添加优质多元复合酶的洗衣液综合效果明显，可以</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:blue\">清除汗渍、泥渍、青草渍、奶渍、食物污渍</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">，<span lang=\"EN-US\">PH</span>值近中性，容易过水，不伤衣物，质量不好的则会对衣物造成伤害，还存在过水难，易残留等问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:blue\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">产</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n黑体;color:#00B050\"> </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:36.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">品</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n黑体;color:#00B050\"> </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:36.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">问</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n黑体;color:#00B050\"> </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:36.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">答</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:36.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：芦荟超浓缩洗衣液</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">能将顽固的污垢洗掉</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">吗？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：能。因为洗衣液里的蛋白酶，能将顽固的污垢溶解，轻而易举地洗掉。建议先涂上洗衣液覆盖污垢，加快分解，然后再浸泡<span lang=\"EN-US\">15--30</span>分钟，洗涤效果更佳。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：芦荟超浓缩洗衣液对人体皮肤有害吗？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：不会。因为它是以芦荟提取物及温和表面活性剂等原料研制而成，不会对人体皮肤产生伤害。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">3、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：增艳剂有何用？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：增艳剂能使一些有颜色的衣物</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">越洗越鲜艳</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，白色的衣物洗后保持其自度而不变色。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">4、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：完美芦荟超浓缩洗衣液为什么在清洁衣服的同时可以保护我们的肌肤？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：因为它</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">不含磷及无机助洗剂</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">，性质温和，且添加了芦荟精华提取物，呵护娇嫩肌肤。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">5、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：为什么用芦荟超浓缩洗衣液洗衣服可以</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">延缓衣服的破旧时间</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：因为它含有环保型特效衣物增艳剂<span lang=\"EN-US\">--</span>天来宝<span lang=\"EN-US\">CBS&mdash;X</span>，使浅白色织物或颜色鲜亮的衣物，保持洁白艳丽，即使反复洗涤虽旧犹新。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">6、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">问：完美超浓缩洗衣液有</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">消毒杀菌</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">作用吗？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">答：有。因为它含有<span lang=\"EN-US\">DP&mdash;300</span>特效杀菌剂，可有效杀灭各种害细菌，消除来自细菌分解所产生的</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">体臭</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">7、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: 