dent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-bidi;color:#339966\">注意事项：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#339966\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#339966\">勿接近火源、电源，放置于<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:#339966\">℃</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#339966\">以下干燥处及儿童不易触及的地方，避免阳光直接照射。切勿将空罐戳穿及投入火中燃烧。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-bidi;color:#339966\">功能：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#339966\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#339966\">除污垢及各种污染物、消除异味。<span lang=\"EN-US\">DIY</span>自行操作、简便易行、省时省力，适用各种空调。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-bidi;color:#339966\">使用方法：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#339966\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><spa