" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">深层保湿日霜</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">（深层滋润 持久保湿）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">主要成分：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">植物甾醇油酸酯、甜杏仁油、硬脂酸甘油酯、水解小麦蛋白、糖鞘脂、卵磷酯、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>棕榈酸酯、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>醋酸酯、亚油酸、亚麻酸、柠檬酸<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">功效：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">富含植物精华，补充肌肤所需水分和营养；促进细胞和胶原纤维的新陈代谢；有效保护皮肤皮脂膜，避免引起皮肤敏感；让皮肤回复润滑和弹性，重新形成健康的保护膜。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">使用方法：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">每天早晨洁面后，取适量日霜均匀涂抹于面部和颈部，形成一层保护膜，避免各种有害物质侵害。坚持使用，将使您的肌肤更加容光焕发，更加年轻、健康、有活力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">适用范围：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">中性、干性皮肤。本产品也可以作为化妆前的底霜使用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Anti-Aging Night Cream</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">活细胞晚霜</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">（激活细胞 再生光彩）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">主要成分：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">琉璃苣油脂质体、霍霍巴油、小麦胚芽油、胡萝卜素、甘油、去离子水。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">功效：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">优质的复合型天然活细胞配方（琉璃苣油、霍霍巴油、小麦胚芽油、胡萝卜素）对肌肤细胞的再生有显著效果；加快细胞内外的物质交流，加速细胞再生，刺激细胞更新，促进细胞新陈代谢，延缓肌肤老化过程，使肌肤恢复嫩滑；蕴含丰富的促进细胞生长的营养素和水分，让肌肤在夜间休息时也能得到全面的营养吸收；完美特效锁水因子，能在夜间预防肌肤水分流失；能舒缓、镇定肌肤，缓解一天的疲劳；经常用来按摩，能让肌肤恢复弹性和活力，令肌肤光滑，富有生机。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">使用方法：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">用滋润爽肤水调理肌肤后，取适量的活细胞晚霜均匀涂抹在脸部及颈部，用指腹由里往外、由下往上轻轻地按摩，除了能促进血液循环与细胞新陈代谢，还可让肌肤更好地吸收晚霜的精华。黄金美容时间是从夜间十点至凌晨两点，这段时间，肌肤细胞的新陈代谢最旺盛，让您的肌肤在此时持续享用活细胞晚霜，肌肤会更显年轻、有弹性。每天坚持使用活细胞晚霜，肌肤会得到显著的改善。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">适用范围：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">中性、干性、老化性皮肤。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Moisturizing Mask</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">润肤面膜</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">（补水抗氧化 美白又光滑）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">主要成分：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">矿物水、膨润土、甘油、大豆、天然保湿因子。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">功效：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">深层清洁毛孔的污垢、老化角质、使毛孔舒畅，让肌肤更好地吸收养分和水分；温和收敛毛孔，舒缓肌肤疲劳；具有美白作用；平缓细纹，帮助肌肤维持柔嫩细致的质感；使肌肤瞬间光滑柔软、容光焕发。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">洁净脸部后，将润肤面膜均匀敷在洁净的脸部和颈部约<span lang=\"EN-US\">7~10</span>分钟，用清水彻底洁净后，再用滋润爽肤水调肤，收缩毛孔、镇静肌肤。每星期使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">1~2</span>次，效果更佳。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">适用范围：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#FF3399;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">中性、干性、成熟性皮肤； 本面膜也可以作为眼膜使用。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2TvDPXj4XXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T2IFbPXkFaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2jFzQXdRXXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2hUPcXk0aXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T2CbPQXfdXXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/726086364/T20ZYPXhFaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2o2HQXXtXXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2ys6QXfVXXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2u9NrXdNOXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">完美玛丽艳中干性美容护肤步骤<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">白天<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>夜晚<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤一：清洁<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>柔和洁肤乳<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>柔和洁肤乳<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤二：调理<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>滋润爽肤水<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>滋润爽肤水<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤三：滋养<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>深层保湿日霜<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>防晒美白润肤霜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>活细胞晚霜<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">每周特别护理<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>润肤面膜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>每周使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">2--3</span>次<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">美丽除了气质以外，还应包括皮肤的健康与美丽。人只有一张脸，如何让肌肤健康自然呢？我们根据不同的气候特点和皮肤状态，采取有效护理方法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">干性皮肤的皮脂腺分泌不足，而中性皮肤如果没有长期科学的护理，它的皮脂膜也很容易遭受破坏，不但保湿功能降低，而且皮脂也会变得干燥、发痒，甚至脱皮，对冷热，触压的防御力也跟着减弱，极易引起红肿，局部泛红等现象，本套装所有护肤产品与皮肤一样呈弱酸性，能全面清洁、调理、滋养您的肌肤！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">玛丽艳美容护肤系列产品由世界著名化装品公司法国</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">FBI</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B