span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">PH</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">值呈中性的柔和洁肤乳</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); font-weight: normal; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">适合任何皮肤类型</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，也可用作眼部卸妆，可深层清洁毛孔深处的污垢和残妆，同时为护肤的下一步作好了准备，且不会破坏皮脂膜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#FF3399\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.05pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">取适量柔和洁肤乳于指尖，均匀涂抹于脸部，用指腹从脸颊到颈部以螺旋方式轻轻打圈按摩，再用温水洗净或用湿化妆棉由内侧往外侧小心擦净。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#FF3399\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">去除污垢就是尽量不让污垢留在脸上，所以每天至少用柔和洁肤乳早晚各洗<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>次，会使您的肌肤更亮丽动人。从容易附着污垢的<span lang=\"EN-US\">T</span>字区着手，小部位如发际与下巴处，也要仔细清洗，颊骨周围及纤弱的眼睛部位迅速清洗即可，包括细微部在内，要多冲洗几次。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 51, 153); font-family: 华文仿宋; font-size: 13.5pt;\">请使用温水，以免毛细孔紧闭，影响清洁效果。并注意在洗脸过程不可用力揉擦皮肤。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2wqGlXhBcXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/726086364/T2NFnBXjxaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2AFYIXdJaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T29GPFXodaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2LaDyXoRaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2GcrIXbVaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">完美玛丽艳中干性美容护肤步骤<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">白天<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>夜晚<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤一：清洁<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>柔和洁肤乳<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>柔和洁肤乳<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤二：调理<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>滋润爽肤水<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>滋润爽肤水<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤三：滋养<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>深层保湿日霜<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>防晒美白润肤霜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>活细胞晚霜<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">每周特别护理<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>润肤面膜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>每周使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">2--3</span>次<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">美丽除了气质以外，还应包括皮肤的健康与美丽。人只有一张脸，如何让肌肤健康自然呢？我们根据不同的气候特点和皮肤状态，采取有效护理方法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">干性皮肤的皮脂腺分泌不足，而中性皮肤如果没有长期科学的护理，它的皮脂膜也很容易遭受破坏，不但保湿功能降低，而且皮脂也会变得干燥、发痒，甚至脱皮，对冷热，触压的防御力也跟着减弱，极易引起红肿，局部泛红等现象，本套装所有护肤产品与皮肤一样呈弱酸性，能全面清洁、调理、滋养您的肌肤！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">玛丽艳美容护肤系列产品由世界著名化装品公司法国</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">FBI</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-la