XXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2yRNTXeReXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/726086364/T2kSLJXiJXXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2i4zJXddaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T2_1DJXeRXXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美玛丽艳中干性美容护肤步骤<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">白天<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>夜晚<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤一：清洁<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>柔和洁肤乳<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>柔和洁肤乳<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤二：调理<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>滋润爽肤水<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>滋润爽肤水<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤三：滋养<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>深层保湿日霜<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>防晒美白润肤霜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>活细胞晚霜<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">每周特别护理<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>润肤面膜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>每周使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">2--3</span>次<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">美丽除了气质以外，还应包括皮肤的健康与美丽。人只有一张脸，如何让肌肤健康自然呢？我们根据不同的气候特点和皮肤状态，采取有效护理方法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">干性皮肤的皮脂腺分泌不足，而中性皮肤如果没有长期科学的护理，它的皮脂膜也很容易遭受破坏，不但保湿功能降低，而且皮脂也会变得干燥、发痒，甚至脱皮，对冷热，触压的防御力也跟着减弱，极易引起红肿，局部泛红等现象，本套装所有护肤产品与皮肤一样呈弱酸性，能全面清洁、调理、滋养您的肌肤！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">玛丽艳美容护肤系列产品由世界著名化装品公司法国</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">FBI</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">（生产兰蔻和雅思兰黛的公司，玛丽艳是其第三个系列产品）授权完</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-