r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">为什么晚上要使用晚霜：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">晚上面部的皮肤处于新陈代谢活跃期，进行分裂和繁殖，需要更多的水份和养分，玛丽艳活细胞晚霜含优质的复合型天然活细胞配方能满足皮肤补充额外水份的需要，使肌肤柔软有弹性并防止水份散失。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\ncolor:#FF3399\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">用滋润爽肤水调理肌肤后，取适量的活细胞晚霜均匀涂抹在脸部及颈部，用指腹由里往外，由下往上轻轻的按摩，除了能促</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 华文仿宋; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">进血液循环与细胞新陈代谢，还可以让肌肤更好地吸收晚霜的精华。</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#FF3399;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">黄金美容时间是<span lang=\"EN-US\">22:00--02:00</span><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，因为这段时间肌肤细胞的</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#FF3399;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">新陈代谢最旺盛，让您的肌肤在此时持续吸收活细胞晚霜，肌肤会显得年轻，有弹性。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T2SzjeXdlbXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/726086364/T2ti8wXaNOXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2q7LyXolaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T281W1XhxXXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2HfCeXjBcXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/726086364/T2PPbLXedaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/726086364/T2G4PDXaFaXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/726086364/T2IeeEXj0cXXXXXXXX_!!726086364.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美玛丽艳中干性美容护肤步骤<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">白天<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>夜晚<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤一：清洁<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>柔和洁肤乳<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>柔和洁肤乳<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤二：调理<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>滋润爽肤水<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>滋润爽肤水<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">步骤三：滋养<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>深层保湿日霜<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>防晒美白润肤霜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>活细胞晚霜<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">每周特别护理<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>润肤面膜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>每周使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">2--3</span>次<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">美丽除了气质以外，还应包括皮肤的健康与美丽。人只有一张脸，如何让肌肤健康自然呢？我们根据不同的气候特点和皮肤状态，采取有效护理方法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">干性皮肤的皮脂腺分泌不足，而中性皮肤如果没有长期科学的护理，它的皮脂膜也很容易遭受破坏，不但保湿功能降低，而且皮脂也会变得干燥、发痒，甚至脱皮，对冷热，触压的防御力也跟着减弱，极易引起红肿，局部泛红等现象，本套装所有护肤产品与皮肤一样呈弱酸性，能全面清洁、调理、滋养您的肌肤！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp; &nbsp