ition: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">棕榈酸酯等。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">功效：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清爽配方，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">适合油性和混合性皮肤使用</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，蕴含柔和的洁净因子，能彻底清洁毛孔中的污垢及残妆；促进细胞的新陈代谢，同时保持肌肤的</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">持久清爽、洁净</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">；有效预防粉刺、暗疮的产生；减少毛孔阻塞和黑头，同时平衡油脂分泌，帮助镇定和舒缓肌肤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">早晚将清爽洁面乳抹于面部，用湿的手指在面部轻轻打圈，然后用温水洗净。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清爽紧肤水</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">成分：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">去离子水、芦荟提取物、甘油、柠檬酸、<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">D-</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">泛醇、丙二醇、乳酸、山梨酸钾、尿囊素等。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">功效：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清爽配方，不含酒精，可进一步洁净面部，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">软化角质层</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，促进新陈代谢；控油因子，吸除毛孔多余油脂，有效</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">收敛粗大毛孔</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，调理肌肤；活性植物提取成分可有效镇静肌肤，减少皮肤出现过敏现象，令肌肤清爽润泽；有效补充水分及平衡皮肤的<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">pH</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">值，使用后肌肤倍加清爽。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">洁肤后，用化妆棉蘸取适量清爽紧肤水，轻拍于面部和颈部（眼部周围除外）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清爽凝胶</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">成分：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">去离子水、山梨醇、丁二醇、甘油、金合欢醇、乳酸、金缕梅提取液、柳树皮提取物、丝氨酸、太阳花籽油、<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">D-</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">泛醇、维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">棕榈酸酯、红没药醇等。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">功效：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">不含油分，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">适合油性和暗疮皮肤使用</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，可有效护理肌肤；清爽配方，有效补充水分，让肌肤自由呼吸；具有减轻红丝现象、镇静肌肤的功效，预防粉刺及暗疮的发生；</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清爽不油腻</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，经常使用可使肌肤润泽光亮。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">洁肤、调肤后，取适量的清爽凝胶均匀抹于脸部。对需要补水的皮肤可使用在平衡晚霜前。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">平衡晚霜</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">成分：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">去离子水、丁二醇、辛酸<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">癸酸三甘油酯、甘油、乳酸钠、金合欢醇、柳树皮提取物、太阳花籽油、金缕梅提取液、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">D-</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">泛醇、红没药醇、尿囊素等。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">功效：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">蕴含植物的活性成分，深层滋润皮肤；有效平衡皮肤的油脂分泌，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">保持肌肤油水平衡</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，预防毛孔的阻塞；减少皮肤问题的产生，并</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">加强皮肤的修复能力</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">；妆前使用，更容易上妆，并让妆容更持久。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">晚上洁肤、调肤后，取适量的平衡晚霜均匀抹于脸部，也适合油性皮肤在化妆前使用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">深层洁肤面膜</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">成分：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">去离子水、高岭土、甘油、金合欢醇、霍霍巴油、山梨醇、<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">D-</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">泛醇、维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">棕榈酸酯、红没药醇、维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">E</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">醋酸酯、太阳花籽油、尿囊素等。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">功效：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清爽配方，含控油因子，可有效</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清除毛孔阻塞</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，预防粉刺、暗疮的发生；快速溶解毛孔内的污垢和吸除多余油脂，达到平衡油脂分泌和调节皮肤<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">pH</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">值的功效；深层清洁皮肤，能为肌肤提供所需养分，并有效美白；持续使用，可明显</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">改善肌肤暗淡、粗糙及疲劳</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">等现象，使肌肤亮白润泽。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">洁肤后，取适量的深层洁肤面膜均匀抹于面部（眼部周围除外），保留大约<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">10--15</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">分钟，然后用指腹轻轻地揉掉，再用温水彻底清洗干净。请按需要每星期使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1--2</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">次。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:48.2pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美护肤品问答<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:48.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n24.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">1、<span