t; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">③</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">干性皮肤</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">--<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">也是选择</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">滋润护肤品</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">系列，由于干性皮肤缺乏水分和滋润，所以干性皮肤的护理重点在于保湿和滋养，晚上用活细胞晚霜做适当的按摩，给皮肤足够的滋润，一个星期敷用<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1--2</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">次的润肤面膜来保湿。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">④</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"