nitial initial;\">滋润护肤品</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">系列产品的基础上，应再加上</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">活力精华露</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">等特效产品，护理的重点在于保湿和滋润，增加弹性，延缓皮肤衰老的过程。每天晚上用活细胞晚霜做适当的按摩，能促进血液循环，增强皮肤吸收能力，激发细胞的复制能力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">⑥</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 楷体_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">混合性皮肤</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">--<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">兼有两种以上不同性质的皮肤，护理的重点在于清洁皮肤、改善肤质，预防皮肤问题日益严重。治疗方法必须</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">针对不同的部位使用不同的产品</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">进行护理。才能达到明显的疗效。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">除了以上基本的皮肤护理，我们还要做好</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">防晒</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的措施，特别是在夏天，每天外出时必须涂上玛丽艳防晒美白润肤霜来预防紫外线对皮肤的伤害。此外，还要注意自身的调理，如：保持均衡的饮食、足够的水分、充足的睡眠、适当的运动和愉快的心情，这样才能达到护肤的最佳效果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">问：男士也能使用玛丽艳护肤品吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\