nt-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品代号：<span lang=\"EN-US\">MA6042<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品规格：<span lang=\"EN-US\">75ml/</span>支</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">248</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/scjfmm.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#B2A1C7;mso-themecolor:accent4;mso-themetint:153\">清除毛孔阻塞，预防粉刺、暗疮<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:126.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:7.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;color:#B2A1C7;mso-themecolor:accent4;mso-themetint:153\">----</span><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;color:#B2A1C7;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent4;mso-themetint:153\">完美玛丽艳深层洁肤面膜<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">成分：去离子水、高岭土、甘油、金合欢醇、霍霍巴油、山梨醇、<span lang=\"EN-US\">D-</span>泛醇、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>棕榈酸酯、红没药醇、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>醋酸酯、太阳花籽油、尿囊素等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">功效：清爽配方，含控油因子，可有效清除毛孔阻塞，预防粉刺、暗疮的发生；快速溶解毛孔内的污垢和吸除多余油脂，达到平衡油脂分泌和调节皮肤<span lang=\"EN-US\">pH</span>值的功效；深层清洁皮肤，能为肌肤提供所需养分，并有效美白；持续使用，可明显改善肌肤暗淡、粗糙及疲劳等现象，使肌肤亮白润泽。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n华文仿宋;color:#00B050\">使用方法：洁肤后，取适量的深层洁肤面膜均匀抹于面部（眼部周围除外），保留大约<span lang=\"EN-US\">10--15</span>分钟，然后用指腹轻轻地揉掉，再用温水彻底清洗干净。请按需要每星期使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">1--2</span>次。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/86904047/T2SzLhXfBaXXXXXXXX_!!86904047.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">面</span><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">膜</span><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">问</span><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">答</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n18.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">问：什么时间使用面膜最好？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">答：使用玛丽艳深层洁肤面膜或润肤面膜最好的时机是沐浴的时候，因为沐浴时的水蒸气会使您的毛孔张开，便于面膜发挥清洁毛细孔深处的多余油脂、污垢及细菌的功效。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">问：深层洁肤面膜具有保湿功效，它能代替润肤面膜吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">答：深层洁肤面膜的主要功效是净白和油水平衡，它所提供的保湿效果只是辅助性的。如果肌肤出现起屑、脱皮等缺水现象，仍需使用润肤面膜加强肌肤的保湿效果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">3、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">问：每周可使用深层洁肤面膜几次？能与脱角质霜同一天使用吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">答：深层洁肤面膜能吸收脸部肌肤表面及毛孔深处多余的油脂，但每周使用以不超过两次为宜。因为，虽然皮肤需定期进行深层清洁，但过频过度去除皮肤油脂，从而刺激皮肤，令皮肤可能出现红肿、干燥或发痒等过敏现象。脱角质霜同样具深层清洁效果，若与面膜同一天使用，则过度洗去皮肤天然油脂，使肌肤丧失天然防御功能。因此建议两种产品不在同一天使用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">4、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">问：如果我使用面膜和脱角质霜，还需要每天使用洁肤啫喱吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">答：洁肤啫喱属于基本护理用品，需每天使用两次，以清洁皮肤，利于清爽凝胶、平衡晚霜的吸收，深层洁肤面膜和脱角质霜属于每周特别护理用品，能深入清洁毛孔内污垢，去除皮肤表面老死细胞，可视皮肤状况而选择使用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">5、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">问：面膜可用于眼部周围吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">答：玛丽艳润肤面膜因具滋润功效可以作为眼膜使用，而深层洁肤面膜使用时应避开眼部和唇部周围。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:63.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">6、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">问：深层洁肤面膜与脱角质霜有何差别？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">答：玛丽艳深层洁肤面膜与脱角质霜均可深入清洁皮肤。脱角质霜能通过搓揉而去除肌肤表皮的死细胞，加速肌肤的新陈代谢，使粗糙的肌肤重现平滑，而深层洁肤面膜则能深入清洁皮肤毛孔内的污垢，并吸收多余的油脂。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/436299874/T2HR7aXfNXXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/436299874/T2rUkXXl8aXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/436299874/T2cOQaXXtaXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/436299874/T24LMbXdxXXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/436299874/T2YyXUXn0dXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/436299874/T2o7D6XXlbXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/436299874/T2wdgbXf8XXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/436299874/T20iEaXXBaXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/436299874/T2pyIXXfNaXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/436299874/T2LRobXXdXXXXXXXXX_!!436299874.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(54, 95, 145); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">完美玛丽艳油性美容护肤步骤</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\