t:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">双眸神采，源自活肤<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:24.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#FFCC66\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:24.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#FFCC66\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:24.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ----</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">活肤眼霜</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:24.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">眼睛周围皮肤的特性：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">最薄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">纤细、脆弱；最敏感</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">立即反应因睡眠不足、情绪变化等因素带来的影响；容易干燥</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">皮脂腺、汗腺都很少；容易疲劳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">不断表情变化、眨眼。</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0\">眼睛保养非常重要：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">皮肤的纤细、脆弱，不但较容易受伤害，并且</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">复原非常困难</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">，几乎没有皮脂分泌，少量排汗，导致皮肤非常干燥，肌肤不断活动促成过度疲劳，以上因素生成小皱纹并导致肌肤松弛，同时最会出现浮肿或黑眼圈，因为它能敏感地反映</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">不规则生活</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">带来的负面影响。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">眼睛保养品特性：</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#0070C0;font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">消费者青睐的透明非油性眼部专用护肤品。胶质除了能制造皮膜，保护肌肤免受刺激外，对皮肤的浸透率高，可以使肌肤产生张力。采用含镇静作用的植物成份，能恢复眼睛疲劳。其他活性元素能针对皱纹、黑眼圈、眼袋皮肤松弛，甚至唇部组织加以特别照顾，可有效地延缓老化，预防皱纹出现。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">主要成分：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">不含香精，含有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">DNA-RNA</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">、植物活性脂质体、鳄梨油和大豆油、透明质酸。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0\">功效与特点：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0\">、改善黑眼圈和浮肿</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">防止眼袋产生、修护眼角细纹、防止眼部周围干燥、改善眼角下垂、平滑皱纹、消除眼部周围油脂。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0\">、非油性</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">眼部周围表皮下具有粘膜，一触及油性物质将会出现浮肿现象，所以非油性的眼霜最适合。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0\">、采用植物萃取精华</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">研究显示山金车（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">Arnica</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">）有促进血液循环，使皮肤组织活化的作用，配合七叶树果实（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">Horse&nbsp; Chestnut</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">），大麦（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">Barley</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">），粟子马（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">Ruscus</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">），还可促进新陈代谢，恢复皮肤活力与生机，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">缓解浮肿发炎</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">，改善眼部周围的过敏现象。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0\">、胶原纤维、弹力纤维素</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">含高度保湿因子，有强化肌肤的功效，使皮肤恢复弹性，看起来润泽，防止皱折和萎缩现象。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0\">、纯化大豆萃取甘油</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#0070C0\">Glycerln</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">强力保湿因子提炼自欧洲新鲜大豆，能将空气中水份吸附于表面上，使细胞润泽富弹性。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0\">、天然泥炭矿泉水</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#0070C0\">Natural Moor Nineral Water</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#0070C0\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">含多种医疗特质的植物荷尔蒙、微量元素、抗生素及维他命组合。这些添加元素，填充结缔组织细胞间隙，抑制有脂肪组织的增厚，从而改善眼袋问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#0070C0\">使用方法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">脸部洁净后，用无名指取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">粒米大小的份量直接抹于眼睛周围，用指腹轻轻拍打，使它渗入肌肤，避免拉扯。如果眼睛下方有明显的黑眼圈、眼袋或严重干燥，抹上眼霜后再</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">贴上化妆棉</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">，即以提高渗浸透力，效果更佳。（如不慎入眼，立即用清水冲洗。）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">小心做好眼部周围保养工作，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">岁就开始做好眼部保养，重点集中在</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">眼尾和眼部下侧</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">。坚持每天早晚用眼霜护理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文中宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">抹去岁月痕迹</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文中宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文中宋;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体;color:#00B050;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"> </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文中宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">留住青春风采</span></strong><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文中宋;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">玛丽艳的研究专家在研究中发现，肌肤皱纹产生的重要原因是细胞含水量下降、细胸活力降低、蛋白酶活性不足以及蛋白质自然合成下降。在这一发现的基础上，玛丽艳针对如何防止眼部皮肤产生皱纹的难题，专门推出了含有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">DNA-RNA</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">、鳄梨油和大豆油、植物活性脂质体和透明质酸等成分的玛丽艳活肤眼霜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">玛丽艳活肤眼霜含有珍贵的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">DNA-RNA</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">营养成分，</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#0070C0;font-weight:\r\nnormal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">DNA-RNA</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">是主宰细胞的增殖、新生、修复与新陈代谢的重要关键物质</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">，对身体机能有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">赋活</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">的作用；眼霜中的鳄梨油和大豆油富含维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">A</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">D2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#0070C0\">B</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\">E</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">和卵磷脂等营养成分，能够有效补充眼部皮肤所需的营养并有效抵抗老化；另外，眼霜中的植物活性脂质体可以作为营养物质载体，能够将活跃的抗衰老成分有效地输送至皮肤细胞内，促进胶原蛋白的合成，提高生物利用度，具有长效缓释作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#0070C0\">有专家说，人的皮肤是否美观，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#0070C0;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">透明质酸</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#0070C0\">起了决定性作用，衰老出现的皱纹就是真皮层透明质酸含量降低所致。玛丽艳活肤眼霜所含的透明质酸来自海洋生物提取物，具有优异的保湿功效。该成分能维持皮肤水环境的恒定作用，无论在低温度还是在高湿度条件下，它都具有相同的高吸湿性，并改善皮肤生理条件，为真皮胶原蛋白和弹性纤维的合成提供优越的外部环境，加强营养物质的供给，起到护肤养颜的效果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#0070C0\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;