Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">关于痘痘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 15.75pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">青春痘又叫痤疮、或粉刺，是由于青春期时，体内的荷尔蒙会刺激毛发生长，促进皮脂腺分泌更多油脂，毛发和皮脂腺因此堆积许多物质，使油脂和细菌附着，引发皮肤红肿的反应。其实，青少年不一定都会长痘痘；而痘痘也不一定只长在青少年的身上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 15.75pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">根据长痘原因的小调查，我们发现，饮食不当（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">10%</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">）、荷尔蒙失调（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">16%</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">）、情绪与压力变化（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">13%</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">）、睡眠质量不好（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">13%</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">）也是最常见的长痘原因。此外还有遗传因素、水分不足、保养品使用不当、换季、肝脏机能不佳、清洁习惯不良、紫外线照射，以及健康状况不佳等因素，均造成了痘痘横行霸道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">从皮肤角度来看，痘痘形成的原因</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 15.75pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">一、角质层是皮肤的最外层组织，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">28</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;\r\nmso-themetint:153\">天为最外层角质的一个代谢周期。如果角质层没有正常代谢而变得厚重的话，皮脂腺就无法正常排出，为痘痘的产生提供条件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 15.75pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">二、皮肤的皮脂腺，全年都会分泌油脂，保持皮肤润泽，而春夏季分泌特别旺盛，各人的皮脂腺分泌能力各有不同，油脂分泌特别旺盛的人就是油性皮肤，如果角质层厚重的话，很容易堵塞毛孔，形成痘痘。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#FABF8F;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 15.75pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FABF8F;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themetint:153\">所以，要排除问题肌肤的困扰，需要我们从各方面进行努力。从肌肤护理的角度来看，洁净肌肤，平衡油脂分泌，解决粉刺、暗疮等问题变得极其重要。油性皮肤可选用清爽系列产品，帮助调理油性皮肤。如果因青春发育、荷尔蒙失调等原因产生了丘疹、痘痘等问题，可以针对性地选用完美玛丽艳全新推出的平衡修护液，帮助解决或减少以上问题，让肌肤重新拥有光彩洁净。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 15.75pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 15.75pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/img