olor: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">25</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">能吸收</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">97</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">％的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#FF6699;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">UVB</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">紫外线</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，其先进的物理防晒剂能有效防止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">UVA</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的伤害，提供</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">PFA++</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的保护因子，随时为皮肤提供养份，改善皮肤老化现象，是</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">防晒、保湿、基础护理</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">多种功能结合的护肤品，它的全方位护理是通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">预防、护理、保护</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#FF6699;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">以达到有效抑制色素沉淀，改善肌肤光泽度的功效。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">主要成份：</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">红没药醇、熊果苷、维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">E</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">、芦荟提取物、神经酰胺尿囊素、丁基甲氧基二苯酰甲烷、超微细二氧化钛等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">功效：</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">抑制酪氯酸酶活性，</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">减少黑色素形成</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">；镇静、安抚、抗发炎以助于维持皮肤健康；控制表面过多油脂，以减少污垢并减轻皮肤负担。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">主要特点：</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">去除老化角质细胞，改善肤色，修护受损细胞并提供保湿滋润；保护肌肤不受紫外线的伤害；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">抗氧化以防自由基的伤害</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">使用方法：</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清洁皮肤后，取适量防晒美白润肤霜涂抹于面部和颈部。在出门前做好护肤和防晒措施，你的肌肤才能得到完善的双重保护。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">在烈日下，大约每隔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#FF6699;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF6699;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">小时应重新涂一次防晒美白润肤霜。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:36.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/1097902934/T2THZdXiVaXXXXXXXX_!!1097902934.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/1097902934/T2sZ__XktXXXXXXXXX_!!1097902934.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:48.2pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">产 品 问 答</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">问：完美玛丽艳防晒美白润肤霜中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SPF</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">代表什么？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SPF</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">是防晒系数（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Sun Protection Factor</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">）的英文缩写，表明防晒用品所能发挥的</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">防晒效能的高低</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">。它是根据皮肤的最低红斑剂量来确定的。按照国际通用的分级方法，防晒化妆品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SPF</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">值小于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，表示无防晒效果；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">2--4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">为低级防晒效果；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">4--8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">为中级防晒效果；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">8--12</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">为高级防晒效果；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">12--20</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">为高强级防晒效果；大于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">为超强防晒效果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">问：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SPF</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">值越高防晒效果越好吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">答：根据中国人的皮肤情况，不需要太高的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SPF</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">值的防晒化妆品，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SPF</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">值为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">25</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">就足够了。比如有的标到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SPF</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">值为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">60</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，含量太高，反而会刺激皮肤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">玛丽艳防晒美白润肤霜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SPF</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">25</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，能吸收</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">97</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">％的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">UVB</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">紫外线，其先进的物理防晒剂能有效防止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">UVA</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的侵害，提供</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">PFA+++</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">保护因子，具有高防晒效果，积极防止阳光侵害，</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">预防色斑</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的形成。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">3、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">问：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">青少年可以使用玛丽艳防晒美白润肤霜</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: ini