-family:&quot;楷体_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:fuchsia\">设计：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">一般的眼霜很难</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">消除</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&ldquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">酸、涩、痛、胀</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&rdquo;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">这种看不见但是感觉得到的眼部疲劳。护眼啫喱采用天然绿色配方，复合植物营养精华充分促进循环，长时间营养滋润，芳香精油成分迅速渗透，舒援肌肤紧张。利用周期护理的方式，轻轻松松减缓眼周肌肤压力，提振精神，令心灵享受绿色假期般的放松。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#FFCC66\">眼部肌肤完美全攻略</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">年龄是女人最大的秘密，然而那巧笑嫣然的眼角眉梢却最容易在不知不觉中成为你魅力的叛徒。为什么岁月总是先侵蚀我们的眼睛？我们又怎样与岁月作斗争，多保留一分美好？玛丽艳眼部护理产品将与您一起抚平岁月的痕迹。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">从生理上来看，人的眼睛是脆弱的，而且周围皮肤很薄，仅是脸颊皮肤厚度的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">1/4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，皮脂腺与汗腺分布很少，同时也缺乏丰厚的肌肉层，只有一层薄薄的环状形肌肉。如此脆弱的器官却是五官中最忙碌、最活跃的：它每天不但要完成约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">10000</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">次的眨眼，还要频繁参与微笑、瞥眼、皱眉等活动。同时眼周下沿分布了许多重要的淋巴结，一旦淋巴循环不良就会在该部位形成废物及废水堆积，进而导致皮肤组织松散，皮肤质地粗糙。如果你再有一些不太好的习惯，如常眯眼看东西，说话表情过于丰富，眼部常带有残留化妆品，化妆或卸妆时经常过分拉扯眼部肌肤，就更是雪上加霜了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">这一切导致的后果是：</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">浮肿、黑眼圈、小皱纹及眼袋</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">。如果幸运的你还没遇到这些问题，那你更要细心地呵护，因为不管什么事情，防患于未然总是最有效的。于是从第一次用眼部护理产品开始，我们对眼霜的要求也就越来越升级得不近情理：要求去眼袋、去黑眼圈、防皱、提升、收紧、防晒、美白等等，最好能一应俱全。于是买了又买，试了又试，怎样才能不着痕迹地将岁月拒之门外？玛丽艳眼部护理产品能成为女性朋友们追求梦想的法宝。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">玛丽艳眼部护理产品有两款：</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">活肤眼霜和护眼啫喱</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">。玛丽艳活肤眼霜含有珍贵的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">DNA-RNA </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">营养成分，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">DNA-RNA</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">是主宰细胞的增殖、新生、修复与新陈代谢的关键物质，对身体机能有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">赋活</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的作用；眼霜中的鳄梨油和大豆油富含维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">A </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">D </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">B </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">E</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">和卵磷脂等营养成分，能够有效补充眼部皮肤所需的营养，并有效抵抗老化；另外，眼霜中的植物活性脂质体可以作为营养物质载体，能够将活跃的抗衰老成分有效地输送至皮肤细胞内，促进胶原蛋白的合成，提高生物利用率，具有长效缓释作用，一般适用于干性、中干性以及成熟性肌肤。玛丽艳活肤眼霜将多种活性成分有机地结合在一起，有效促进眼部肌肤的血液循环及细胞再生，在高效补水、保湿的同时，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">有效减缓皱纹的形成，改善黑眼圈，预防眼袋的出现</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，有效抵抗眼部肌肤的老化。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">玛丽艳护眼啫喱采用植物萃取精华，能镇静末梢神经，舒缓肌肤，消除眼部疲劳，并有效预防眼部浮肿、黑眼圈、眼袋的困扰，一般</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">适用于油性、偏油性以及较年轻的眼部肌肤</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">。玛丽艳护眼啫喱同时还可激活细胞新陈代谢，减少眼角皱纹，延缓眼部肌肤衰老，让您的双眸妩媚动人，再现神采。同时采用高科技生化技术提取的纯天然抗衰老添加剂，可促进皮肤细胞新陈代谢，加速受伤皮肤复原。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">拥有天使般的美丽容颜是女人心中永远的梦想，作为传递心