font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品价格：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">480</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/M7035.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:DFKai-SB;color:#00B050;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">年轻肌肤最要<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>紧<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:\r\ntext2;mso-themeshade:128\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;\r\nmso-themeshade:128\">紧致光滑，晶莹剔透的肌肤一直是每一个爱美女性对护肤的终极渴望。色泽正常、滋润平滑、丰满而富有弹性、没有皱纹的皮肤才是健康且富有青春活力的表现，自然会给人带来美感。但人的肌肤会随着年龄的增长而逐渐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:\r\n128\">老化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:\r\n128\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;\r\nmso-themeshade:128\">，皮肤会变得发干、弹性差，以致出现许多皱纹。因此，除了养成良好的饮食习惯、注意劳逸结合、加强身体锻炼、保持心情舒畅外，还需懂得及时对肌肤进行保养及护理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;\r\nmso-themeshade:128\">如何让你松弛的肌肤都变成过去，目前针对老化肌肤的保养，大多只着重在抗皱的领域，并没有关注因为老化所引起的毛孔粗大问题，所以花大钱作保养，以完全保卫青春的留逝。毛孔粗大是最令女士们困扰的事情，就算使用化妆品遮掩，也只是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:\r\n128\">治标不治本</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:\r\n128\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;\r\nmso-themeshade:128\">，要真正解决问题，</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;\r\nmso-themeshade:128\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;\r\nmso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\">惟一的办法是做好基本的肌肤护理，让毛孔自然收紧。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.1pt; line-height: 150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:red\">玛丽艳紧肤精华露的功能：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;\r\nmso-themeshade:128\">蕴含大豆蛋白和杏仁提取物，可有效减少皱纹、收紧肌肤，令肌肤更紧实，光滑细腻；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;\r\nmso-themeshade:128\">富含维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:\r\ntext2;mso-themeshade:128\">A</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;\r\nmso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\">C</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nsimsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:\r\n128\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:\r\n128\">E</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;\r\nmso-themeshade:128\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:\r\ntext2;mso-themeshade:128\">F</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:simsun;color:#0F243E;\r\nmso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\">，可加强皮肤弹性，使娇嫩的肌肤保持青春活力，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;simsun&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#0F243E;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-themeshade:128\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 20.25pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:simsun;mso-far