: 黑体; color: red; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">规格：<span lang=\"EN-US\">150ml</span></span></strong></b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://www.perfect99.com/product_pic/BigImages/2004220163843321.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312, serif; color: rgb(255, 0, 128); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">有机调理<span lang=\"EN-US\">*</span>完美修复<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 42pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">------</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 42pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 黑体; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">黑泥面膜</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">主要成份：深海有机泥、芦荟、海藻、海草、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>、钾、镁、锌、氨基酸酶等。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">功效：清除毛孔内的阻塞物，平衡油脂分泌；深层吸收皮肤内的毒素；刺激表皮血液循环，恢复皮肤光泽度；协助暗疮皮肤复原，且有消炎的功效；多种维生素与矿物质，能补充皮肤所需要的养分。让肌肤美白光滑；淡化暗疮印、色素斑、净化肤质，美白皮肤。黑泥面膜还您一个健康、亮丽的面容。约三万年前，万物丛生，由于洪水泛滥，将许多植物、花草、水果、草药及矿物质淹埋在水下，经过大自然的千锤百炼形成了一种有机泥，这一特殊的有机泥后来经科学家们研究发现，确认它是当代不可多得的护肤瑰宝。玛丽艳黑泥面膜使用的就是这种非常独特的有机泥。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">玛丽艳黑泥面膜以深海有机泥为基料，辅以多种氨基酸活性成分等植物精华精制而成，有机泥中丰富的钾、钠、镁、锌等矿物质均以可溶性离子形式存在，容易渗透肌肤而被吸收，并能增强和均衡皮肤的矿物质。此外，有机泥中蕴含海藻、海草、盐、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>，可以迅速吸收皮肤多余油脂，面膜干涸收缩时，其收紧压力可将痤疮内的油脂和分泌物吸出表皮，清洁并收紧肌肤毛孔，有效改善粉刺倾向性皮肤油脂分泌不平衡的现象，舒缓毛孔粗大、油光满面现象，解除黑头粉刺、白头粉刺、油脂粒的困扰，同时具有良好的保湿、滋养效果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">使用黑泥面膜，可以在短时间内达到深层清洁肌肤、促进血液循环及新陈代谢、消除疲劳的效果，使老化松弛的肌肤充满活力、焕然一新。在使用黑泥面膜过程中，同时使用滋润喷雾，可以缓减面膜干燥速度，调节面膜紧绷度，更好地发挥面膜深层清洁、调理、滋养、美肤效果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">该产品适用于任何性质的皮肤，仅需根据不同的肤质类型确定敷用时间即可，例如：油性皮肤敷用<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>分钟，中干性皮肤敷用<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>分钟，敏感性皮肤敷用<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>分钟。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> <!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br />\r\n<!--[endif]--></span><img src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/152940932/T2N2TlXo0aXXXXXXXX_!!152940932.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/152940932/T2nuvoXXJXXXXXXXXX_!!152940932.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 36.05pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文中宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#E36C0A;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:\r\n191\">玛丽艳面膜 给你一个亮丽的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>面子<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;<i>!!!</i></span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文中宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#E36C0A;mso-themecolor:accent6;mso-themeshade:\r\n191\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">今天，面膜已经成为许多女性必备的美丽工具，只要轻松敷上<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>－<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>分钟，肌肤就会变得光滑紧致。尤其在干燥的秋冬季节，敷面膜更成了必不可少的美容护理，随时为你呈现水灵灵的肌肤。为了让肌肤始终保持良好的状态，你需要深入了解面膜的特性，选择合适的面膜定期为肌肤调理。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">面膜，是利用覆盖在脸部的时间，暂时地隔离外界的空气与污染，同时提高肌肤温度<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>大约<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>度<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，加强血液循环，促进新陈代谢，使肌肤的含氧量上升，变得更有活力。而且在这个时间内，肌肤与身体都获得了彻底的休息，就像短暂的睡眠一样，能够得到放松。此外，在敷面膜的时候毛孔会彻底打开，在清洁肌肤的同时，可以更好地吸收面膜中的营养成分，并增强肌肤对其他护肤品的吸收能力，让你容光焕发。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">面膜依照不同的功能和适合不同的肤质，有多种类型，玛丽艳润肤面膜含有的矿物水、膨润土、甘油、大豆提取物及天然保湿因子等成分，主要适合中、干性及成熟性皮肤，能够清洁毛孔深处污垢、毒素、老化角质等，令毛细孔畅通，及时给肌肤补充丰富的营养和水分，充分滋润肌肤，温和收敛毛孔，平缓细纹，帮助肌肤维持柔嫩细致的质地，还可改善表皮黑色素现象，具有美白作用。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">玛丽艳黑泥面膜则适用任何类型的皮肤，具体可根据不同的肤质类型确定敷用时间。玛丽艳黑泥面膜以深海有机泥为基料，富含多种矿物质及多种氨基酸活性成分，极易渗透肌肤而被吸收，增强和均衡肌肤所需养分；短时间内消除肌肤疲劳，促进肌肤血液循环及新陈代谢，达到深层清洁、平衡油脂分泌、保湿滋养的功效，使肌肤充满活力，焕然一新。同时配合使用滋润喷雾，可以缓减面膜干燥速度，调节面膜紧绷度，更好地发挥面膜深层清洁、调理、滋养、美肤效果。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">选择一款好的面膜，能彻底清除肌肤深处的污垢，促进血液循环，并让肌肤得到全方位的呵护保养，散发健康动人的光泽。赶快行动为自己的肌肤挑选一款合适的面膜吧！</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-align: center; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:red;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">面膜的七大关键问题</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">随着美容护肤行业的不断发展成熟，面膜成为众多爱美人士手中的一大武器，如何更好地利用好手中的这个武器，首先要了解有关它的七个关键问题。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、先洁面，还是先敷面膜？</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">当然是先洁面。用温热的水使肌肤毛孔打开，排出皮脂和污垢后，面膜的营养成分就更容易被皮肤吸收了。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、先用面膜，还是先用化妆水？</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">如果是干性皮肤或气候干燥时，可以先拍丽肤露，后用滋润面膜；如果用清洁面膜则是先敷面膜，后拍丽肤露或平衡紧肤露。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、是否要敷厚厚一层？</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">是的。适当厚度的面膜敷在脸部时，肌肤温度上升，促进血液循环，会使渗入的养分在细胞间更好地扩散开来。肌肤表面那些无法蒸发的水分则会留存在表皮层，让皮肤水分饱满、光滑紧致。温热还会使角质软化，毛细孔扩张，让堆积在里面的汗垢趁机排除。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、面膜可以每天使用吗？</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">如果是清洁面膜，每天使用会造成肌肤敏感，甚至红肿，令尚未成熟的角质失去抵御外来侵害的能力；如果是滋润面膜则会由于营养成分过剩而容易引起暗疮；如果是补水面膜，则可以在干燥的季节里每天使用。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、敷面膜时有刺痛感正常吗？</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">轻微的、一次性的刺痛感是正常的。含有补水成分的面膜在脸极度缺水的状态下使用会有轻微的刺痛感。简易测试方法：先在手肘内侧的皮肤上涂抹少量面膜，<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>分钟后若无过敏反应，则可敷在脸上。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、用过面膜后能否不用面霜？</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">面膜是周期性的护理品，目的是为皮肤补充深层营养。但若没有表面的锁水和滋养，从面膜中得到的养分就会很容易流失掉，因此，敷完面膜后一定要照常涂抹护肤品。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">7</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">、敷面膜的时间是否越长越好？</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">时间过长会导致肌肤失水、缺氧。除了遵照说明书，你可以根据不同的面膜做一个大概的估算：水分含量适中的面膜，大约<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>分钟就卸掉，以免面膜干后反从肌肤中吸收水分；水分含量高的面膜，可以多用一会儿，但最多<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>分钟就要卸掉。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 华文仿宋; font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">相关资料<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:\r\nnormal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">&nbsp;&middot;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">冬季别让面部皮肤<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>感冒<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">拥有完美肌肤的女性是动人的，也最容易给人以精致的感觉，因而爱美女性总是不遗余力保护娇嫩肌肤。然而在瑟瑟的寒风中，身体有厚厚的外套挡寒，而面部皮肤只好露在外面。同样，寒冷的冬日，在暖气房内人会感到舒服，可外出时，冷暖温度的急剧变化，又在第一时间内将皮肤，尤其是面部皮肤从温暖的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>春日<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>拉回到寒冷的冬季。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">其实皮肤也会<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>感冒<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，起皮、发红、发痒、干裂等现象就是症状。只有正确防范才能让皮肤从容应对冬季的寒冷。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">冷水适当刺激。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#000033;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">就像预防感冒一样，为了提高皮肤突然遭遇冷空气的适应力，美容师建议不妨也给皮肤来一个预防运动。由于天气冷，早晨洗脸时，很多人都喜欢用较热的水，其实热水会刺激皮肤毛细血管的正常代谢，很容易形成皮肤的红血丝，带走大量水分。正确做法是先用温水洗脸，以利于清洁皮肤油脂，然后再用冷水，但并不是直接洗脸而是用手将水轻轻拍到脸上，给皮肤一个缓冲的过程，这样持续约一分钟左右，不仅可以有效防止冷空气给皮肤带来的不适，还可以起到收缩毛孔的作用。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">另外，当要从温暖的环境中走出去时，戴上口罩也是保护面部皮肤的有效方法，让保留的温度在冷空气中缓缓释放，也可以给皮肤一定的适应时间。但由于冬季的皮肤比较干燥，很容易受伤，所以口罩一定要保证柔软、干净，以防划破皮肤及细菌的侵入。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">给肌肤正确<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>补水<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">缺水是冬季皮肤的最大敌人，不少人选择利用润肤面膜来给皮肤增加水分，这当然是一种非常直接有效的办法，但是不当的敷面膜方式不仅不会缓解皮肤缺水现象，还会使本来已经很脆弱的皮肤再受伤害。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">有些人认为面膜是补水的，自然是时间越长越好，然而面膜的营养成分一部分通过皮肤吸收，另一部分暴露在空气中自然蒸发。当皮肤吸收饱和后，如果面膜已经变干但还没有及时卸去，面膜反而会将皮肤中的水分带走。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">一般来说，面膜在脸上停留的时间应在十五分钟左右，最长不超过二十分钟。用手掌轻轻接触面膜的脸颊部位，如果这个部位已经没有水分就应该及时卸膜了。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">在空气干燥的空调房中，涂抹润肤霜或是用滋润喷雾及时补充水分，也可以缓解皮肤的干燥，但要注意的是一定要选择不含酒精或酒精含量较小的产品，因为酒精的蒸发会带走大量水分。应在感到面颊较干时使用，如果过度使用会使皮肤细胞鼓胀，容易产生浮肿现象。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm 13.45pt 5.25pt; text-indent: 20.25pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red;font-weight:normal;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">别忽视面部<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>运动<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm 13.45pt 5.25pt; text-indent: 20.25pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">生命在于运动，同样的，皮肤的健康也离不开运动。冬天由于空气变冷，皮肤新陈代谢减慢，很容易晦暗无光，如果保护不当，起皮、发痒等症状也会随之而来，这时可以人为的给皮肤做运动。轻轻地以打圈的形式按摩脸部皮肤，促进皮肤新陈代谢，预防冻伤的情况发生。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#000033;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">按摩时要先涂抹玛丽艳按摩膏或活细胞晚霜，防止干燥皮肤的拉伤，同时动作要缓慢轻柔，特别是皮肤较薄的眼睛周围更要注意。同时在眼角、嘴角、额头等部位做提拉动作。有人感到寒冷时往往下意识地用双手上下搓脸，这样虽然可以促进皮肤血液循环，但却容易拉伤肌肤，一般不可取。</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/894208582/T20qfaXddaXXXXXXXX_!!894208582.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-align: center; text-indent: 52.2pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">黑泥面膜问答<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm 13.45pt 68.25pt; text-indent: -36pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#00B050\">1、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">问：黑泥面膜能否与脱角质霜在同一天使用<span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm 13.45pt 68.25pt; text-indent: -36pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">答：黑泥面膜和脱角质霜都具有去死皮的作用，所以建议错开使用。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm 13.45pt 68.25pt; text-indent: -36pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#00B050\">2、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">问：黑泥面膜是否可以用于颈部？</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm 13.45pt 68.25pt; text-indent: -36pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -36pt;\">答：可以，将黑泥面膜用于颈部能帮助肌肤更光滑白嫩，并提高一定的保湿度，用于全身更好。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm 13.45pt 68.25pt; text-indent: -36pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#00B050\">3、<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">问：黑泥面膜可否敷得更久一些，或者敷过夜？<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">答：我们建议黑泥面膜的敷用时间是<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>分钟左右，然后就用湿水冲洗干净。这个时间是经过研发人员精心测试的，确保</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> 面膜能够发挥其最佳效果。我们不建议敷得更久一些，或者敷过夜。因为皮肤对化妆品的吸收有一定限度，不见得敷得</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">越久越好。面膜完全干透后，如果在肌肤停留时间过长，可能会有不适感觉。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:华文仿宋;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/250_thumb_G_1370060477627.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/250_G_1370060477908.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/250_G_1370060477781