itial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">玛丽艳脱角质<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF0066\">蕴含独特的查帕拉尔橡树提取物、辣木种子提取物、辛基琥珀酸铝淀粉、甘油等主要成分的完美玛丽艳脱角质霜，在成分功能特点上，是一种凝胶型的去角质护肤品，属于水溶性，其胶状质地通过溶解老化角质层达到去除角质的目的。老化角质随着产品摩擦后的碎屑一起被擦除，它蕴含的温和成分能改善肌肤干燥现象，淡化缺水细纹，同时净化肤质，改善肤色，使肌肤变得柔软平滑，透白亮丽。由于其独特的温和性，各类皮肤均适用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#FF0066\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF0066\">主要成分：去离子水、高岭土、聚乙二醇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#FF0066\">-8</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#FF0066\">、鲸蜡硬脂醇、聚二甲基硅氧烷、硬脂酸、失水山梨醇棕榈酸酯、棕榈酸、聚山梨醇酯、辣木种子萃取物、灌木提取物、聚丙烯酸树脂、苯氧基乙醇、尼泊金甲酯、香精、乙二胺四乙酸二钾等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#FF0066\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF0066\">功</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#FF0066\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF0066\">效：温和去除皮肤表层的死皮、杂质，畅通毛孔，改善粗糙肌肤；促进肌肤新陈代谢，增强细胞吸收养分及排泄废物的功能；净化肤质、改善肤色、美白肌肤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#FF0066\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF0066\">使用方法：先用玛丽艳洁肤啫哩清洁脸部，待皮肤干后，在脸部和颈部敷上薄薄一层脱角质霜。待干后（约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#FF0066\">1--2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#FF0066\">分钟）用手腹轻轻揉去脱角质霜，然后用清水洗干净，再拍上清爽紧肤水。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:26.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:黑体;color:#00B050\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:黑体;color:#00B050\">产 品 问 答</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:47.25pt;text-indent:-20.25pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">1、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">问：脱角质霜可否用于全身性的护理？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">答：玛丽艳脱角质霜不仅可以用于脸部，也可以用于身体其它部位，以去除粗糙的表皮，令全身肌肤更光泽、细致。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:47.25pt;text-indent:-20.25pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">2、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">问：使用脱角质霜会令皮肤更薄、更容易受紫外线伤害吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">答：玛丽艳脱角质霜能加速表皮细胞剥落和新细胞的生长，但不会改变皮肤的天然构造，所以不会令皮肤变薄。不过使用后，皮肤表面老化的角质层剥离，显露出新鲜的细胞，如果不注意防晒，可能易受到紫外线伤害，所以在使用后应再使用防晒美白润肤霜，并避免在阳光下过度暴晒。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:47.25pt;text-indent:-20.25pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:0;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#00B050\">3、</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#00B050\">问：深层洁肤面膜与脱角质霜有何差别？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-farea