r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/1667885611/T2xPRrXfVOXXXXXXXX_!!1667885611.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/1667885611/T20ev.XmRaXXXXXXXX_!!1667885611.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/1667885611/T2mIzSXXFaXXXXXXXX_!!1667885611.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 26pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">滋润保湿修复干燥脱皮双手</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<i><span style=\"color:#FF3399\">-------</span></i></span><b><i><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#FF3399\">维</span></i></b><b><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#FF3399\">E</span></i></b><b><i><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#FF3399\">润手霜</span></i></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.5;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><i><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">纤纤玉手，结缘于水</span></i></strong><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#FF3399\"><o:p></o:p></span></i></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">很多人在保养肌肤的时候，往往忽略了一个重要的部分，那就是手的护理。只精心修饰了面部、头发和服饰，却露出一双粗糙、遍布皱纹的手，就好象一段完美的音乐中混入了一个不和谐的音符，让人尴尬。完美玛丽艳维<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>润手霜特别为缺乏保养的干性及粗糙的双手而准备。它含有的天然植物精华，能</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); font-weight: normal; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">软化硬皮，修复干燥脱皮</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的双手，能渗透到细胞深处，提供营养和水份，充分滋润保湿，并有效隔离含刺激性洗涤用品和恶劣天气变化，例如油污、灰尘对手的伤害。持续使用，能恢复白皙皮肤，使双手柔滑细嫩，润泽健康，含天然植物精华和植物美白成份，能调理肌肤，改善肤质，令双手看起来更年轻，形成一层滋润保护层，使皮肤柔软、光滑，含特效保湿脂类基质，为肌肤补充水份并防止水份散失。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#FF3399\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">主要成分：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">去离子水、甘油、辛基十二烷基肉豆蔻酸酯、鲸蜡醇辛酸酯、丁二醇、芒果籽油、氢化聚葵烯、微晶蜡、单硬脂酸甘油酯、鲸蜡硬脂醇、沙棘果油、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>、聚二甲基硅氧烷、失水山梨醇倍半油酸酯、尼泊金甲酯、苯氧基乙醇、香精、乙二胺四乙酸二钠等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">功效：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">蕴含沙棘果油和绿茶中多种活性养分，迅速渗透肌肤，补充所需营养，促进细胞新陈代谢，减轻自由基对肌肤的伤害，保持肌肤弹性，改善肌肤粗糙问题，</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: normal; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">预防干裂</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">。同时多种保湿成分，使肌肤保持润泽、细腻光滑而富有弹性，增添手部线条的柔美魅力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">清洁双手后，取适量的润手霜，均匀涂抹于双手（</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); font-weight: normal; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">采用由内向外的螺旋式按摩</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">），让肌肤更好地吸收其精华。每天使用润手霜，您的纤手会得到大大改善，女人不仅要保护自己的俏脸，更应当加倍护理您的纤纤玉手，如果有一双粗糙的手，无论如何都会影响您个人的气质与魅力，在我们手背上只有很少的皮脂腺，必须经常</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); font-weight: normal; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">补充油份和水份</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 153); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，否则手会变得粗糙，因此，无论冬夏，润手霜是靓女化妆袋中必备之物。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#FF3399\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/252_thumb_G_1370059903630.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/252_G_1370059903734.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/252_G_1370059903499.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '29', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1370755368', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
