rgb(0, 176, 80); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用方法：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">沐浴后，将适量的身体保湿乳均匀地抹开至全身，同时轻柔地按摩肌肤，让保湿乳完全被肌肤吸收，需要时可随时使用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">在寒冷冬季，皮肤的保养应该更注重在润泽，以避免皮肤过于干燥。由于寒冷干燥的冬季来临，人体皮肤角质层水份含量减少，皮肤就会随之失去细腻和弹性，变得粗糙，若长期得不到护理，很容易老化，出现各种皮肤异常现象。而在炎热的夏季，由于阳光的暴晒或长期处于空调环境中，皮脂腺、汗腺的分泌会很旺盛，无形中加快了肌肤水份的流失，因此，要保持皮肤的健康美丽，首先要</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); font-weight: normal; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">补充角质层水份</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">含量。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">事实上，皮肤会自然产生所需要的保湿因子，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">切正常情况下，健康的皮肤有制造本身所需的所有基本成份的能力。但是，皮肤无法抵抗年龄、生活形态及环境所造成的伤害，保湿因子却因生活方式和环境条件等因素而枯竭，所以防止肌肤干燥，必须补充肌肤水份。完美玛丽艳维</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">E</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">身体保湿乳含有最新最有效的多种天然保湿因子，与健康肌肤所发现的十分类似，其精华的天然性质能捕捉与皮肤表层细胞接触的外在水份并保存于细胞内。您可将其想象成一块海绵，能为皮肤吸取并保存水份。保湿因子犹如额外的水份储备，使保湿乳涂在肌肤上一段时间后，仍可为肌肤提供所需水份，滋润成份不含油脂，改善肤质，均匀肤色，减少并平滑细纹，令全身肌肤增强弹性和改变松驰状况，令肌肤看起来更光滑，更年轻，充满活力。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(255, 51, 204); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/253_thumb_G_1370059506913.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/253_G_1370059506733.jpg', 'images/201306/so