3;\r\nmso-themeshade:191\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:accent3;\r\nmso-themeshade:191\">功</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:accent3;mso-themeshade:191\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#76923C;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent3;mso-themeshade:191\">效：含有丰富的滋养保湿成分，性质温和细腻，适合脸部和身体的按摩；促进血液循环和新陈代谢，消除肌肤疲劳，增强肌肤对营养物质的吸收能力；滋润保湿，润而不腻，使用后令肌肤轻盈柔软、活力倍增。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:\r\naccent3;mso-themeshade:191\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:accent3;\r\nmso-themeshade:191\">适用范围：脸部、身体肌肤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:accent3;mso-themeshade:191\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#76923C;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent3;mso-themeshade:191\">小贴士：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:accent3;\r\nmso-themeshade:191\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#76923C;mso-themecolor:accent3;mso-themeshade:191\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#76923C;\r\nmso-themecolor:accent3;mso-themeshade:191\">一年四季，受紫外线等恶劣天气侵蚀的肌肤极易疲劳，甚至有些人因暴晒、刮风等，导致皮肤红肿或水肿等炎症发生。这种受到严重损伤的肌肤，由于角质层水分不足，也容易引起皮肤干燥和代谢功能的紊乱。如置之不理，就会成为促使皮肤老化，产生皱纹、黑斑及雀斑的罪魁祸首。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:\r\naccent3;mso-themeshade:191\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:accent3;\r\nmso-themeshade:191\">为使皮肤保持青春活力，对皮肤进行适当的按摩是不可缺少的护理方法。晚上睡觉前泡一个澡，是在一天结束之际不可缺少的放松步骤；刚洗完澡，全身还很热的时候做按摩，作用会更明显：如果是局部按摩，也可先用热毛巾敷在皮肤上。在进行按摩前应先涂上适量按摩膏，使用一段时间后你会发现按摩膏保养肌肤的效果非常显著，因为这不但可以促进血液循环，刺激体内毒素排出体外，使皮肤得到充分休息，消除疲劳，还可以给肌肤深层提供养分，可以起到养颜除皱，防止衰老的功能。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:\r\naccent3;mso-themeshade:191\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:accent3;\r\nmso-themeshade:191\">玛丽艳按摩膏含有丰富的滋养保湿成分，性质温和细腻，适合脸部和身体的按摩。定期使用能增进血液循环，给皮肤组织补充营养；增加氧气的输送，促进细胞新陈代谢的正常进行；帮助皮肤排泄代谢废物，排除积于皮下过多的油脂，清除肿胀和皮肤松弛现象，有效地延缓皮肤衰老的作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:\r\naccent3;mso-themeshade:191\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:#76923C;mso-themecolor:\r\naccent3;mso-themeshade:191;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 只要您坚持用玛丽艳按摩膏进行按摩，那么玛丽艳按摩膏的滋养成分和按摩作用相辅相成，就会令您的肌肤充满青春活力，让您的肌肤变得与众不同的光滑。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/254_thumb_G_1370059416497.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/254_G_1370059416795.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/254_G_1370059416704.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '27', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1370752853', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
