N-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:13.45pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:13.45pt;margin-left:\r\n0cm;text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">澳州坚果油、芒果籽油能快速渗透肌肤，延缓脂质体的过早氧化，保护皮肤细胞膜的稳定性，从而使肌肤柔软、保湿并增强肌肤天然弹性；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:13.45pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:13.45pt;margin-left:\r\n0cm;text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">芦荟萃取液深层渗入唇隙，持久锁住水分，令双唇时刻保持水嫩，更具舒缓情绪紧张提神的作用；维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>有效抵御自由基侵害，预防唇部肌肤过早老化； 自然绿茶清香带来怡人享受；搭配玛丽艳唇膏使用，可增加唇膏亮度，妆扮完美唇色<span lang=\"EN-US\">!<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/55577561/T2MfYVXelXXXXXXXXX_!!55577561.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#0D0D0D;mso-themecolor:\r\ntext1;mso-themetint:242\">玛丽艳<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Marie Anne)</span>是世界知名化妆品公司法国<span lang=\"EN-US\">France Beaute Industrie(FBI)</span>的著名品牌。<span lang=\"EN-US\">France Beaute Industrie</span>，创建于<span lang=\"EN-US\">1921</span>年，最初以生产香水为主。<span lang=\"EN-US\">1971</span>年正式进军美容护肤行列，至今已生产出一系列知名品牌的美容护肤化妆品，如玛丽艳， 玛丽艳畅销全世界二十多个国家，深受爱美人士喜欢。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#0D0D0D;mso-themecolor:\r\ntext1;mso-themetint:242\">完美凭借一流的设备和严格的管理体系赢得该公司青睐，已被正式授权为亚太区唯一生产和销售玛丽艳美容护 肤品的企业。玛丽艳美容护肤品是在全面引进法国<span lang=\"EN-US\">FBI</span>公司配方、独特的生产工艺及主要原材料的基础上，针对东方人的肌肤特点，采用优质纯天然植物精华及国 际尖端美容护肤配方研制而成。为东方人士提供更专业、更完整的滋养和保护，其有效成分更容易被皮肤吸收，令肌肤充满健康活力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\ncolor:#0D0D0D;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:242;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">玛丽艳的美容化妆品系列包括：敏感修护系列、滋润系列、清爽系列、 特别护理系列、彩妆系列。</span></strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/55577561/T2nhvVXeBXXXXXXXXX_!!55577561.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">1.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">世界十大专业护肤品牌</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">玛丽艳走专业化的路子，是通过美容院客户对它的反映评比出来的，产品不走商场不做广告。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.1pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">2.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">纯植物性产品<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">选用天然植物精华，国际尖端美容配方，独特的工艺技术，有效成分容易吸收，无论是洁肤、爽肤、润肤还是特效护理产品都是精华为主，加上肌肤所需要的各种活性元素用高科技配制。<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.1pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">3.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">修护型产品<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">护肤品分保养和修护型两种，保养只起到清洁、保养功效，对皮肤上出现的问题没有较好的改善作用，玛丽艳护肤品是修护型产品，有对一般皮肤改善，问题型皮肤针对性改善修护的功效。<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">4.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">安全性<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">玛丽艳的产品有清、调、补的作用，有一个适应过程，如出现反应，有专业美容顾问进行处理，并且能把皮肤中重金属的东西调理出来。市面上的产品大多数铅、汞、砷超标，而玛丽艳绝对不含任何化学物质，三十多年来，<span lang=\"EN-US\">FBI</span>公司的产品没有做坏过任何一张脸。<span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">5.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">多功能</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">如：洁肤乳不仅能起到洁肤的作用，同时也可以去掉专业的彩妆<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &nbsp;</span>活肤眼霜：淡化皱纹、黑眼圈、脂肪粒</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">6.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">经济型</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">同类品质价格比较低<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">7.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">服务</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;a) </span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">购买前我将为您详细讲解产品<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &nbsp;b) </span>购买中教你如何正确有效的使用<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &nbsp;c) </span>购买后，提供一定售后服务，随时咨询。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;<