感；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n            line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n            mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">高纯度的时尚色彩，配合多孔粉末，加强色彩在唇部的延展性与附着性，让您的双唇令人怦然心动。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n            0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:26.0pt;\r\n            line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n            minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">完美<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>唇<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>情</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:26.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n            宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n            0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <div align=\"center\">\r\n            <table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100.0%;border-collapse:collapse;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;\r\n                mso-padding-alt:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\n                        font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">唇，是微笑的起点，是牵动鲜活表情的关键。柔润美唇，绝不仅仅是抹上亮丽的色彩就可以成就的。拥有润泽、紧致、饱满的健康双唇，是打造一切极致美唇的先决条件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\n                        mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n                        宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\n                        font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">唇部皮肤的黑色素少，表皮较薄，对干燥的空气、低温、冷风等环境特别敏感。同时，说话、微笑、吃东西、抽烟都会导致嘴唇四周过早产生皱纹。所以，这个干燥的早春。不妨动手为双唇的靓丽下点功夫吧！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\n                        mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n                        宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\n                        font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">卸妆，完美唇情第一步<span lang=\"EN-US\">!</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n                        line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n                        minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\n                        font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">即使是最不擅长化妆的人，也会使用口红。一项数据表明，唇部是平均化妆时间最长的一个部位，没有好好地卸妆，长期积累在嘴唇缝隙中的口红会渐渐地阻碍唇部肌肤正常代谢，让唇色加深变黑，甚至导致唇部肌肤纹路加深。尤其唇部有油脂分泌腺无小汗腺，彩妆卸除不干净，污垢不会被汗水自动溶解掉落，久而久之，嘴唇便会呈现老态，因此，完整的唇部卸妆，是打造美唇的首要。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\n                        font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">保养，完美双唇最关键<span lang=\"EN-US\">!<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\n                        font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">嘴唇比眼部肌肤更脆弱。它没有毛发、汗腺，甚至角质层也不完整，除了年纪带来的皱纹之外，任何外来的刺激、污染，过热或过冷的天气，都会让它招架不住。所以日常的唇部保养是非常有必要而且是必须的一项工程。建议每天使用润唇膏并随身携带润唇膏，因为润唇膏会随着时间的流逝、喝水、饮食而脱落，当唇部感到涩涩时，就应补搽润唇膏。同时定期给双唇来个集中保养，比如一周做一次唇膜也能大大改善唇部干燥问题。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\n                        font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">玛丽艳新一代润唇膏含有多种滋润双唇的成分<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;&mdash;</span>葡萄籽油、澳洲坚果油、芒果籽油、芦荟萃取液、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>等。葡萄籽油具有超强的抗氧化能力及营养功效，可有效修复胶原蛋白组织，全面滋润肌肤，预防唇部出现干燥、脱皮、皲裂现象；澳洲坚果油和芒果籽油能快速渗透肌肤，延缓脂质体的过早氧化，保护皮肤细胞膜的稳定性，从而使肌肤柔软、保湿，并增强肌肤天然弹性；芦荟萃取液能深层渗入唇隙，持久锁住水分，令双唇时刻保持水嫩；维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">E</span>可有效抵御自由基侵害，预防唇部肌肤过早老化，真正实现唇部肌肤的内在保养；润唇膏的自然绿茶清香，能带来怡人的享受。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\n                        font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">呵护，靓丽双唇小帖士<span lang=\"EN-US\">!<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n                        150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">◆ </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n                        宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n                        mso-font-kerning:0pt\">加强面部护理：口角松垂，与唇部肌肉的松弛有关。面部除了需要滋润外，还需要水分和营养来增加皮肤的张力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n                        150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">◆ </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n                        宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n                        mso-font-kerning:0pt\">注意保护牙齿：如果牙齿和牙床不健康，唇部也会过早老化，唇部的健康亦会受到影响。所以，一定要防止蛀牙和牙周病，每天必须认真刷牙，及时去除牙病，使美唇无后顾之忧。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n                        150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">◆ </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n                        宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n                        mso-font-kerning:0pt\">常锻炼下巴肌肉：嚼口香糖是锻炼下巴肌肉的好方法。要注意左右两边交替，以保持面部两边肌肉的运动量平均，可避免唇部肌肉松弛。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n                        150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">◆ </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n                        宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n                        mso-font-kerning:0pt\">维生素和水让唇部更柔润<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\n                        line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\n                        minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">日常要多喝水，食用含有丰富维生素的蔬菜和水果，还可适量服用维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>、维生素<span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span>，这些都可改善唇色暗沉，让双唇变得健康润泽。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\n                        line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n                        150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n                        mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">◆ </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n                        宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red;\r\n                        mso-font-kerning:0pt\">指压唇部穴位：唇部的疲劳实际上是感觉不到的。消除唇部疲劳的有效方法是穴位指压。在唇部周围的穴位，稍用力按压，保持<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>秒钟，可加速血液循环，消除肌肉疲劳。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n                        宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n                        0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbs