\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/1(10).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"1854\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">无论是女人还是男人，优雅的，内涵十足的，品位特别的，香水也许就是自己心情的流露。那些有色或透明的液体，夹杂着诡异的清香、伤感、野性、颓废、优雅，唤起了人们不同的感受和回忆。西方人把使用香水形容为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">穿香水</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，选择一款适合自己的香水，掌握一套</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">穿香水</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">的哲学，那性感美妙的完美香氛，会让你魅力四射。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 22.1pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#948A54;mso-themecolor:background2;mso-themeshade:128\">香水锦囊</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#948A54;mso-themecolor:background2;mso-themeshade:128\">&mdash;&mdash;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#948A54;\r\nmso-themecolor:background2;mso-themeshade:128\">如何选购香水</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#948A54;mso-themecolor:\r\nbackground2;mso-themeshade:128\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">香水世界有几个基本的调系：芳香的、清新的、摩登的、古典的、神秘的等等。如何找到一种适合自己的香味呢？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">选购香水时，最好避免闻太多的香水，因为嗅觉疲劳后很难分出香水的差异，所以最多只闻三种。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">选购香水时，一般先试的部位距离越远越好，左右手腕和手肘内侧，每处可各试一种香水，并记住涂抹位置，以便过后选择。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">3. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">试完香水后，至少等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">分钟，待酒精挥发掉才知道香水真实的气味。</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">最好是离开香水柜台一会儿（因为通常那里混杂了其它香水味），也给自己一个较清净单纯的嗅觉环境，再一次对这种香水</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">进行一番</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">考验</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">4. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">不要在剧烈运动后或饭后试用香水，因为体温和食物的味道会影响香水的味道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">5. </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">不要以为别人身上好闻的香味就一定适合你，香水在不同人身上有着细微的差别</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:22.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#948A54;mso-themecolor:background2;mso-themeshade:128\">香水的最佳涂抹部位</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:22.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#948A54;mso-themecolor:\r\nbackground2;mso-themeshade:128\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.1pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#351C75\">香水吸引人的秘诀在于正确的使用技巧，擦香水只要用无名指，轻轻的在动脉跳动处压两次就可以了，如手腕、脚踝、膝后、脖子、耳后</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#351C75\">&hellip;</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#351C75\">.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#351C75\">让香气自然的散发出来。皮肤容易过敏的人可把香水改喷在内衣、手帕、裤脚或领带内侧，随着肢体的摆动而散发；而腋下与汗腺发达的部位切勿使用香水，否则香水与体味混合，会带给人恐怖的感觉</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#404040\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#351C75\">耳后</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#351C75\">--------</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#351C75\">因头发与头部的遮挡可避免阳光直射，涂少量的香水即可。随风飘过时淡若游丝的香味易令人回味。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.1pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#351C75\">胸（左侧）</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#351C75\">--------&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#351C75\">涂于心脏上方的效果较佳，但因是自己鼻子最易闻到的地方，用量要适当控制</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27.1pt; line-height: 150%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#351C75\">手肘内侧</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:#351C75\">-------