sp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n24.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">-----</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">维他命、糖及蛋白质</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">葡萄糖是人类维持生命、强身健体不可缺少的营养成分，是人体能量的主要来源。葡萄酒中还有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">24</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">种氨基酸，是人体不可缺少的营养物质。葡萄酒中的有机酸成分也不少，如葡萄酸、柠檬酸、苹果酸，大都来自葡萄原汁，能够有效地调解神经中枢、舒筋活血，对脑力和体力劳动者来说，都是不可缺少的营养物质。干红葡萄酒中还含有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">Ve</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">Vb</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">VB2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">等多种维生素和钙、镁、铁、钾、钠等多种矿物质，其中矿物质与多种微量元素集合起来，远胜于最优质的矿泉水。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:24.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">红酒中的多酸含量相当多，因此它对于预防心血管疾病有极好的作用，有助于防动脉硬化和早老性痴呆症等疾病，还具有减少骨质疏松症的危险和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">驻颜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">等重要功效。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">在一般人的观念里，生活上的享受似乎总是身体健康背道而驰的，葡萄酒向我们证明了，只要不过度，享受和健康原是可以兼得的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">1992</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">年，美加流行闰，病学家区艾</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">利森（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">C ELLISON)</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">指出：在法国，人们经常食用富含脂肪类食品，法国人平均胆固醇含量也都不低于其它国家，但法国患癌症死亡的比例，在各工业化国家中却是最低的，它的发病率只为美国的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">60</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">％，而且平均寿命比美国人长寿的秘方，就在于经常饮用葡萄酒，以及其它饮食和生活习惯的协调。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一、葡萄酒的保健作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、增进食欲</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">葡萄酒鲜艳的颜色，清澈透明的体态，使人赏心悦目；倒入杯中，果香酒香年鼻；品尝时酒中单宁微带涩味，促进食欲。所有这些使人体处于舒适、欣快的状态中，有利于身心健康。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、滋补作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">葡萄酒中含有糖、氨基酸、维生素、矿物质。这些都是人体必不可少的营养素。它可以不经过预先消化，直接被人体吸收。特别是对体弱者，经常饮用适量葡萄酒，对恢复</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">健康有利。葡萄酒中的酚类物质和奥立多元素（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Oligoe Lement</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">），具有搞氧化剂的功能，可以防止人体代谢过程中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">?</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">生的反应性氧（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">Ros</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">）对人体的伤害（如对细胞中的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">DNA</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">RNA</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">的</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">伤害），这些伤害是导致一些</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">退化性疾病，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">如白内障，心血管病、动脉硬化、老化的因素之一。</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">因此，经常饮用适量葡萄酒具有防衰老、益寿延年的效果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、助消化作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">蛋白质最优良佐餐饮料。葡萄酒能刺激胃酸分泌胃液，每</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">60-100</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">克葡萄酒能使胃液分泌增加</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">120</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">毫升。葡萄酒中单宁物质，可增加肠道肌肉系统中平滑肌肉纤维的收缩，调整结肠的功能。对结肠炎有一定疗效。甜白葡萄酒含有山梨醇，有助消化，防止便秘。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、减肥作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">葡萄酒有减轻体重的作用，每升干葡萄酒中含</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">525</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">卡热量，这些热量只相当人体每天平均需要热量的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1/15</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">。饮酒后，葡萄酒能直接被人体吸收、消化，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">小时内全</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">部消耗掉而不会使体重增加。所以经常饮用干葡萄酒的人，不仅能补充人体需要的水分和多种营养素，而且有助于减肥。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、利尿作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">一些白葡萄酒中，</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">酒石酸钾、硫酸钾、氧化钾含量校高，具利尿作用，可防止水肿和维持体内酸碱平衡。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、杀菌作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">很早以前，人们就认识到葡萄酒的杀菌作用。例如：感冒是一种常见的多发病，葡萄酒中的抗菌物质对流感病毒有抑制作用，传统的方法是喝一杯热葡萄酒或将一杯红葡萄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">酒加热后，打入一个鸡蛋，搅拌一下，即停止加热，稍凉后饮用。研究表明：葡萄酒的杀菌作用是因为它含有抑菌、杀菌物质。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 二、葡萄酒对某些疾病的辅助治疗作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、葡萄酒与心血管病的防治</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">葡萄酒中的原花色素，能够稳定构成各种膜的胶原纤维，能抑制组氨酸脱羧酸避免产生过多的组氨，降低血管壁的透性防止动脉硬化。另外，原花色素梗</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">塞死亡的危险。据美国医学研究会统计资料表明：喜欢饮用低度葡萄酒的法国人、意大利人，癌症死亡率最低，而喝烈性酒多，葡萄酒少的美国人、芬兰人癌症死亡率很高。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、葡萄酒对脑血栓的防治作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">葡萄酒中含有白藜芦（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">Resveratrol</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">它是一种植物抗毒素，具有抑制血小板凝集作用。葡萄酒中的藜芦存在于葡萄皮上，是一种到杉新</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">?</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">葡萄配糖体，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">红葡萄酒中每升含</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">微克左右，而在白葡萄酒中只含</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">微克。实验表明：即使将红葡萄酒稀释</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">1000</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">倍，对抑制血小板的凝集作用仍然有效，抑制率达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">42</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">％，可减少脑血栓的发生。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、葡萄酒可防治肾结石</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">德国科学家在研究中发现，适量饮用葡萄酒可以防止肾结石。慕尼黑大学医学研究所的医学家们最近指出：多饮用饮料可以防止肾结石的传统说法并不科学，也不全面，最</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">重要的是要看饮用何种饮料，通过对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4.5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">万健康人和病人的临床观察，研究人员确认，经常饮用适量葡萄酒的人，不易得肾结石。研究人员发现，适量饮用不同饮的人，得肾结石的风险也不一样，每天饮用四分之一公升咖啡的人，得肾结石的风险要比无此习惯的人低</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">％；常饮红茶则要低</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">14</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">％；而常饮葡萄酒的人得肾结石的机会最少</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">，得病的风险要比无习惯的人低</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">36</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">％。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、葡萄酒可预防乳腺癌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">最新试验结果显示：以葡萄酒饮料，喂养已诱发得了癌症的老鼠，发现葡萄酒对癌细胞有强烈的抑制作用。美国伊利诺斯药科大学的研究人员，选用了桑椹、花生、葡萄皮中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">抗癌活力最强。美国科学家最近了现，葡萄酒里含有一种可预防乳腺癌的化学物质，位于旧金山葡萄酒研究所的罗伊</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">?</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">威廉姆斯在华盛顿举行的记者招待会上说，他们在红葡萄酒和白葡萄酒中发现一种有预防乳腺癌作用的物质。这一物质这所以有这种功效，是因为它能抗雌激素，而雌激素与乳腺癌有关。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、葡萄酒能抑制脂肪吸收</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">日本科学家发现，红葡萄酒能抑制脂肪吸收，有老鼠作试验，老鼠饮用葡萄酒一段时间后发现，其肠道对脂肪的吸收变缓，对人作临床试验，也获得同样的结论。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、红葡萄酒防治视网膜变性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">美国哈佛大学研究发现：红葡萄酒有防止黄斑（视肉膜）变性的作用。黄斑变性是由于有害氧分子游离，使肌体内黄斑受损，而葡萄酒，特别是红葡萄酒中含有能消除氧游</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">离基的物质</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">白黎芦醇，能保护视沈觉免受其害。试验证实：经常饮用少量红葡萄酒的人，患黄斑变性的可能性比不饮用者低</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">％。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、葡萄酒有助于提高记忆力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">科学家公布的试验结果表明：适量饮用葡萄酒，有助于提高大脑记忆力和学习能力。两位来自米兰大学的医生经进大量实验发现，适量饮用葡萄酒将促进大脑内产生一定量化学物质，这种物质能促进一种与神经细胞记忆有关的生成。据测定：饮用葡萄酒后这种的生成量比未饮者增强大脑的记忆力和学习能力。另一位医生发现，肥胖患者在减肥期间适当饮用葡萄酒，将保持旺盛的精力，不会因为节食而萎靡不振，导致记忆力减退。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、葡萄酒能防治感冒</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">至今全世界对流行性感冒尚发无良策，因为流行性感冒的病毒对大多数药物都有抗药性。但是，人们发现：常饮葡萄酒的人群中，很少感冒。这理现象引起注意，他们把红、白葡萄酒和葡萄原汁加在病毒培养液中进行试验，结果是：单纯疱疹病毒各柯萨奇病毒等常见感冒病毒，在葡萄酒和原汁中都可</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">丧失活力，其中葡萄皮浸出的原汁效果最好。科学家认为，这是因为葡萄含有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">苯酚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">类化合物，能在病毒表体成一层薄膜，使其难以进入人体细胞，从而达到防治感冒的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">效果。由于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">苯酚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">主要存在葡萄皮上，</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">所以感冒时，饮用热的红葡萄酒，可减轻感冒症状和预防感冒。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#7030A0\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">完美（中国）日用品有限公司</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: red;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">荣誉出品</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><b style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">中国食品发酵工业研究院</span></b><b style=\"co', 'images/201306/thumb_img/271_thumb_G_1370064103362.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/271_G_1370064103174.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/271_G_1370064103957.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '10', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1370734558', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
