n lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">2013</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">25</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">日，中国品牌完美拉格诺葡萄酒亮相南非德班第五届金砖五国首脑会议的欢迎晚宴。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">2013</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">25</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">日，中国品牌完美拉格诺葡萄酒作为南非德班第五届金砖五国首脑会议的欢迎晚宴唯一指定用酒华彩亮相。继此次国家领导人出访所掀起的服装产品</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">国产品牌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">热后，完美拉格诺葡萄酒在金砖五国峰会的亮相，再度引起了来宾对中国企业走向世界的关注。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">在金砖五国峰会晚宴上，完美拉格诺葡萄酒是唯一指定接待用酒，其显眼的中文标识额外引人注目。作为晚宴中唯一的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">中国品牌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">，拉格诺葡萄酒的品质亦备受来宾赞誉。完美公司董事长古润金作为唯一企业家代表上台向南非总统雅各布</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">&middot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">祖马赠送特制的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">3L</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">拉格诺西拉红葡萄酒。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">据悉，今年金砖五国峰会的主题为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">金砖国家与非洲：致力于发展、一体化和工业化的伙伴关系</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">，金砖国家领导人将就加强金砖国家伙伴关系、深化金砖国家与非洲合作以及共同关心的国际和地区问题深入交换意见。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">1994</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">年以来，葡萄酒业一直占据着南非重大经济改革和转型的核心地位，在南非的经济发展中发挥着关键性作用，并为南非的经济增长做出了实质性贡献。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">2011</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">17</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">日，在南非政府的见证下，完美与南非猎豹酒庄合资成立</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">完美南非酒业有限公司</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">，揭开了完美公司赴南非投资的序幕。近两年的实践证明，完美公司在非发展取得了良好的成效，成为了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">中国企业走进南非</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">的成功典型之一。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nTahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">作为全国百家明星侨资企业，完美公司在国内蓬勃发展的同时，积极响应国家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">走出去、引进来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">号召。两年来，经完美进口并销售的南非葡萄酒，已占南非全国同期出口葡萄酒总量的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\">50%</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Tahoma;mso-hansi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">以上。完美公司在带给中国消费者优秀葡萄酒的同时，对促进中非民间经贸往来做出了积极贡献。随着金砖五国峰会的召开，完美公司将继续加强在南非的投资与合作，为中非贸易多元化发展做出更大贡献。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/1(4).jpg\" width=\"489\" height=\"626\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/2(4).jpg\" width=\"487\" height=\"609\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/3(3).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"1032\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2011</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span>日，南非前总统德克勒克应邀请首次访华，出席<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>德克勒克中国行<span lang=\"EN-US\">&mdash;&mdash;</span>完美之夜<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，现场见证完美（中国）有限公司下属子公司</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#7030A0;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">──</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">扬州完美日用品有限公司与南非猎豹酒庄合资成立<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>完美南非酒业有限公司<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，用以开拓南非葡萄酒在中国的消费市场，并为中国消费者带来更多高性价比的优质葡萄酒。成立后的完美<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>南非<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>酒业有限公司主打中高端产品市场，还将全权负责德克勒克每年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span>瓶限量签名酒的生产与销售。南非前总统德克勒克表示：<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>完美公司与南非酒庄的结合，相信会是一个完美的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&lsquo;</span>联姻<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rsquo;</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">完美（中国）日用品有限公司</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: red;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">荣誉出品</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Verdana, Arial; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">中国食品发酵工业研究院</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: red;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">监制</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#7030A0;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\"> </span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/272_thumb_G_1370062846794.gif', 'images/201306/goods_img/272_G_1370062846275.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/272_G_1370062846630.gif', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1369456004', '9', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1370732726', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check` ) VALUES  ('273', '35', 'LS', '拉格诺西拉红葡萄酒', '+', '20', '12', '', '9999', '750.000', '680.00', '680.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '200', '', '', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">拉格诺西拉红葡萄酒产品说明</span></b></h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品代号：<span lang=\"EN-US\">LS09<o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">产品规格：<span lang=\"EN-US\">750ml/</span>瓶<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">建议零售价：￥<span lang=\"EN-US\">738</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/1.gif\" width=\"329\" height=\"220\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/11.gif\" width=\"257\" height=\"232\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:36.0pt;font-family:华文中宋;color:#948A54;\r\nmso-themecolor:background2;mso-themeshade:128\">乐梦迪和猎豹庄<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0\">乐梦迪与猎豹庄是两个各具特色的酒庄，但它们都是由位居世界前<span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span>名富豪之列的南非<span lang=\"EN-US\">Rupert </span>家族拥有的物业，是对南非经济影响举足轻重的家族之一。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#7030A0\">Rupert </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#7030A0\">家族的辉煌成就是由已故商业奇才<span lang=\"EN-US\">Anton Rupert </span>博士创造的，出身贫寒的他，白手起家创立了世界顶级奢侈品上市公司<span lang=\"EN-US\">Richemont</span>。他不仅出资协办了世界保护野生动物基金会，他也是南非洲和平主义的积极倡导者。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0\">乐梦迪和猎豹庄是<span lang=\"EN-US\">Rupert </span>家族物业里其中两个精品葡萄园<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>另外两个<span lang=\"EN-US\">L\'Omarin </span>庄和<span lang=\"EN-US\">Rupert &amp; Rothschild Vignerons)</span>。其中乐梦迪创立于<span lang=\"EN-US\">1695 </span>年，是南非历史最悠久的酒庄之一。它的酒以优雅、高贵和经典而著称，被称为&ldquo;和谐的贵族艺术品&rdquo;。庄园座落在南非主要的葡萄酒产区风景秀丽的弗兰谷<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Franschhoek Valley)*</span>。这里得天独厚的优质土壤和稳定的微型气候都赋予乐梦迪优厚的先天潜质，而这种潜质正是被<span lang=\"EN-US\">Anton Rupert </span>发掘了出来，并为乐梦迪名扬海外甚至媲美法国的顶级酒庄打下坚实的基础。乐梦迪精益求精，是致力于超越奖项之上的世界级葡萄酒。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0\">现在乐梦迪庄园由创始人<span lang=\"EN-US\">Anton Rupert </span>的女儿<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hanneli Rupert-Koegelenberg </span>拥有，并由她的丈夫<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hein Koegelenberg </span>掌管。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hanneli </span>是一位南非著名的女<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0\">中音歌唱家，她在频繁地到世界各地演出的同时，也为她的乐迷带来了乐梦迪庄园的风情，乐梦迪成为越来越多人喜爱的葡萄酒。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#7030A0\">由<span lang=\"EN-US\">Anton Rupert </span>和其女婿<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hein Koegelenberg </span>共同创立的猎豹庄虽然没有乐梦迪那样悠久的庄园历史，但凭借<span lang=\"EN-US\">Rupert </span>家族丰富的酒庄经营及品牌打造的成功经验，猎豹庄很快得到国际市场的认可。猎豹酒庄得名于雄浑的开普山猎豹，从它的名字就能感觉到，这是一个充满活力的、年轻而又个性的酒庄。同样座落于弗兰谷的猎豹庄，其产品富有浓郁的花果香味，入口甜美，感觉热烈澎湃，是南非新派葡萄酒的代表作，主要针对年轻、时尚一族的市场。猎豹庄引以为豪的是，它是保护开普猎豹基金会的主要赞助者，致力于保护开普山猎豹。每售卖一瓶猎豹庄葡萄酒，就有一份善款直接拨入该基金会，用于拯救濒危动物南非开普山猎豹。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#7030A0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/2(3).jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"487\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/3(2).jpg\" width=\"634\" height=\"473\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/4(2).jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">一六八八年法国胡格诺派新教教徒来到了南非开普殖民地，他们带来了先进的农耕和工匠技术，在开普殖民地倍受欢迎并丰富了南非早期文化，他们在制酒上的贡献至今仍被人所赞赏。这款酒酒体醇厚，辛辣扑鼻，透出八角、丁香及黑胡椒的辛香，伴有浓郁的黑樱桃和蓝色浆果香味，余韵优雅。此款酒于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span>年灌装，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2014</span>年开始为最佳饮用时间。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#404040\">葡萄品种：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#404040\">西拉<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"