ass=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:30.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">珍贵配方，独一无二 为健康加油！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n30.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:red\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:30.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n黑体;color:red\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:30.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"font-size:27.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:red\">完美营养配方油</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">营养配方油产品经中国农科院油料作物研究所专家团队</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">年精心研发、国家权威机构鉴定认证，服务国人膳食健康，特别针对营养高需求人群的油脂需要，甄选多种珍贵油脂，有机地将不同营养特性的草本油料和木本油料相结合。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma\">完美营养配方油甄选</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">5</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">种非转基因的珍贵油脂，详细如下：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">一、油茶籽油</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">:</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">东方橄榄油，俗称为&ldquo;月子油&rdquo;或&ldquo;育子油&rdquo;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、茶油，是从木本油料植物</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">--</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">油茶树的果实提取而成。油茶树是我国的珍稀资源，盛果期需</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">6-8</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">年，从开花到成熟要历经秋、冬、春、夏、秋五季之雨露，饱含日月精华集天地灵气于一身。成熟于次年花开时节，花果同株并茂，民间有&ldquo;抱子怀胎&rdquo;之佳称，堪称人间奇果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、在中国民间产茶油的地方，历来都有妇女怀孕、产后使用茶油的习俗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma\">茶油中的不饱和脂肪酸含量高达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">90%</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">，高于橄榄油；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma\">茶油中含有丰富的维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">E</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma\">和角鲨烯，同时含有橄榄油中所没有的生物活性物质如山奈酚、多侧链酚类等；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma\">茶油适合烹炒煎炸，符合中国人饮食习惯，相比橄榄油，高温下味道更好。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">二、亚麻籽油</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">:</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:#00B050\">最补脑的天然食物</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、亚麻籽油是我国华北、西北高寒地区种植的主要油料作物之一，其含有丰富的&alpha;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">亚麻酸，含量高达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">55%</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">，是目前已知陆地上亚麻酸含量最高的植物之一。亚麻酸是构成人体脑细胞的重要成分，因而，亚麻籽油被认为是陆地上最补脑的天然食物，它对婴幼儿的智力发育、青少年提高记忆力、中老年健脑以及预防老年痴呆均具有重要的作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、亚麻籽油的特别功能：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma\">促进胎儿及少年儿童的脑部、视力的发育；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma\">保护心脑血管健康；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma\">辅助预防痛风性关节炎。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">三、玉米油：抑制胆固醇的美容食用油</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、玉米油以其独有的玉米清香与不油腻的口感特点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">而深受喜爱。玉米油是目前植物油里面，植物甾醇含量最高的油。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、植物甾醇能抑制人体对胆固醇的吸收、促进胆固醇的降解代谢、抑制胆固醇的生化合成。植物甾醇对皮肤具有很高的渗透性，可以保持皮肤表面水份，促进皮肤新陈代谢、抑制皮肤炎症，可防日晒红斑、皮肤老化。因而也被誉为&ldquo;美容食用油&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">四、核桃油：源自&ldquo;长寿果&rdquo;的食用油</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、一提到核桃，大多数人，尤其是孕妈妈们都知道，核桃是健脑的。其实核桃还有很多其他的功用，中医自古以来就将核桃称为&ldquo;长寿果&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、研究表明，核桃油的磷脂，对脑神经有良好保健作用，核桃油中含有不饱和脂肪酸，有防治动脉硬化的功效。核桃仁中含有锌、锰、铬等人体不可缺少的微量元素。经常食用即能养身体又能抗衰老。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nTahoma;color:#00B050\">五、葡萄籽油：风靡欧美的保健品</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#00B050\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">1970</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">年，法国波尔多大学马斯奎博士，成功的从葡萄籽中提取了纯正原花青素（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">OPC</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">）。科学研究证明，原花青素的抗氧化能力是维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">C</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">20</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">倍，维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">E</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">50</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">倍，而且无任何副作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">1995</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">年以后风靡欧美日本等发达国家，几乎成为家庭必备的健康品。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">、葡萄籽油中含有丰富的脂溶性维生素</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">E</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">以及多酚类物质，亚油酸含量达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">70%</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">以上。亚油酸是人体必需而又为人体所不能合成的脂肪酸。同时，葡萄籽油还能防治心血管系统疾病，降低人体血清胆固醇和血压。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-