i-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">，提取人参中主要的功能成分</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">──</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">人参稀有皂苷精炼而成，人参稀有皂苷在人参中的含量极其稀少，且对人体具有独特的保健作用。小小滴丸，粒粒精品，滴滴金贵！</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:华文中宋;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">[</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">产品优势<span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、稀缺性：人参滴丸是目前世界上唯一应用含有人参稀有皂苷单体制成的滴丸产品，也是国内</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">10639</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">种保健食品中，第一款人参滴丸的品种。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、显效性：产品舌下含服，见效快速显著。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、安全性：人参滴丸剂型小，服用方便，对肠胃无刺激。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">[</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">人参的功效<span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、调节中枢神经系统。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、促进大脑对能量物质的利用，提高记忆能力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、改善心脏功能。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、降血糖作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">[</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">人参皂苷的功效<span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span>：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">人参皂苷（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#404040;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">ginsenoside</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">GS)</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">是人参的主要有效成分，现已明确知道的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">GS</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">单体约有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">40</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">余种，在人参中的含量在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\ncolor:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4%</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">左右。众多研究表明，它具有较高的抗肿瘤活性，对正常细胞无毒副作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">人参皂苷通过调控肿瘤细胞增殖周期、诱导细胞分化和凋亡来发挥抗肿瘤作用。将肿瘤细胞诱导分化成正常细胞有利于控制肿瘤发展，诱导肿瘤细胞凋亡使细胞解体后形成凋亡小体，不引起周围组织炎症反应。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">增强机体的免疫功能。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">提高抵御能力，增强机体的应激能力和适应性。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">抗肿瘤作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">抗氧化作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">【人参滴丸的功效】：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">由于滴丸中含有珍贵的人参皂苷</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\">Re</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">和</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif;\">Rg2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">，自然表现出其非凡的作用。抗疲劳、改善心肌功能、增加大脑心脏氧气供应量、改善睡眠、增加机体抵抗力、改善记忆力下降、预防帕金森综合症和老年痴呆、调节血糖、改善性腺功能、提供生活质量，可以称之为全效型保健品，是中老年人、白领、企业家、司机、学生等必备。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、增强心脏效率</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">扩张心脑血管，抑制血小板凝集和血栓形成，增加血流量，提高供血率，避免因动脉硬化引起的脑萎缩和老年痴呆，降低中风发病率。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、避免心脏抗氧化损伤</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">促进心肌细胞生长，帮助受损心肌复原，避免心脏抗氧化损伤及不正常心率的发生，预防心脑血管疾病的复发、恶化、减轻心脑血管疾病的症状。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:blue;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、调节心律</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">调节神经中枢兴奋与抑制的平衡，延缓神经细胞衰老，抑制心血管中过氧化脂质的形成，改善睡眠质量，提高工作与学习效率，提高记忆力和思维能力，缓解亚健康状态。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、预防记忆力下降</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">可快速改善心脏功能，改善心脑供血。双向调节中枢神经，缓解紧张、焦虑，有镇静、安神作用。促进脑神经分化发育，加速损伤神经的恢复，对智力、记忆力有明显改善。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、改善紧张焦虑</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">从多方面改善紧张焦虑及记忆力下降症状，通过提高心脏功能、调节中枢神经状态、修复受损神经、调节内分泌等途径来消除紧张，达到镇静、改善睡眠的效果。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、提高机体抗氧化能力</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">增加骨髓细胞修复和蛋白质合成，提高肌肉组织细胞抗氧化能力，抑制运动所致自由基增加和脂质过氧化反应，提高机体抗缺氧能力。抑制运动后血清乳酸</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">升高，增强造血功能，缓解疲劳。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">7</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、抗肾疲劳</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">人参滴丸能调节性机能高级中枢神经的紧张，及时调补性活动中物质代谢及能量消耗，彻底消除性生活中的一切疲劳。对有明显的性生活疲劳感的人群，服用人参滴丸后，第二天精力、体力充沛，能满足正常工作。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">8</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:fuchsia;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、抗糖尿病疲劳</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">多数糖尿病患者，由于体内长期营养不良，长期体能透支，下午精神萎靡不振，浑身无力，服用</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">人参滴丸后会有明显改善。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;color:#404040;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:2.0gd;\r\nline-height:150%\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#B45F06;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">注意事项：</span></u></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:blue;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:2.0gd;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">正确服用方法为舌下含服，通过舌下丰富的毛细血管和粘膜直接被静脉吸收，起效快、避免了对肠胃的刺激和肝脏的首过效应，克服了传统服用人参方法起效慢、药效低的不足，提高了有效成分的利用率</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n2.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">适宜人群：易疲劳者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n3.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">不适宜人群</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">: </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">少年儿童</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n4.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">服用人参过敏者忌服</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n5.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">肝阳上亢、脑出血倾向者忌服</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n6.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在患感冒发烧、咽喉干燥和化脓性炎症期间忌服</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n7.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">五心烦热者慎用和减量服用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n8.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">不能与藜芦、五灵脂同时服用，不要用茶水送服，服用二小时内不要吃生萝卜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n9.</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">服用后感觉疲劳状态有明显改善时，可减量服用，每次可服</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">2-3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">粒或</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">4-6</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">粒，最大服用量为每次</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">粒</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color