ly:黑体;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<div class=\"marginleft\" style=\"margin-left: 14px; font-family: Simsun;\">\r\n<div id=\"txt_ulli\" style=\"width: 706px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span id=\"Label_Content\">\r\n<p class=\"text7_em\" style=\"clear: both; line-height: 20px; text-indent: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">美丽肌肤是爱美女性永恒不变的追求，为了让自己永远的年轻、靓丽，我们总是苦苦寻找着属于自己的美容佳品。有没有属于呵护肌肤的至尊宝贝，让美丽永远安然无恙？美容专家告诉我们，美丽使者当属脸部护理安瓶。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">安瓶原意为浓缩精华，是属于真空包装的精华液，看起来像注射针剂的护肤品。它浓度极高，其中对皮肤的有效因子，至少有<span lang=\"EN-US\">90%,</span>甚至达<span lang=\"EN-US\">98%</span>，几乎是晚霜或营养霜的好多倍。安瓶是一种超浓缩精华素，是美容品中的极品<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>它可以让肌肤在最短的时间内达到最佳的状态。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast\">大家可能都经历过一些特殊场合或时间，例如拍新娘照、结婚当天、模特儿时装秀、参加重要宴会晚会等，专业化妆师会在化妆前用安瓶先镇定保养肌肤，把肌肤调理到最完美的时候再上妆。经过如此<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>恶补<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>的肌肤会收紧、含水性好，比平时容易上妆、贴妆并不易脱妆。另外，当肌肤处于极度不舒服或不正常的情况时，比如说，因季节的交替而变得粗糙干燥，或因过度压力，使肌肤变得非常疲倦，或是在长途旅行、长时间暴晒之后，皮肤原本的均衡遭到破坏；甚至由于年龄或荷尔蒙的改变，连面膜都补救不了时，就该试试这种产品了。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"text7_em\" style=\"clear: both; line-height: 20px; text-indent: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">安瓶在妆前使用，可以使皮肤快速变得细腻、白皙，并且起到控油保湿和定妆的作用，在瞬间可改善肤质，使妆面干净透亮，有层次感。同时，也可以把它当作平时保养皮肤的精华素，根据皮肤需要来使用。安瓶还有安内抚外的功能<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>当你的肌肤出现严重问题时，一方面要尽量补充肌肤所需要的营养、水分，强化肌肤天然抵抗力，抵御外界环境的侵害，让肌肤尽快恢复正常；另一方面，加速细胞的修护与更新，提供细胞必需的氧气，带动皮肤新陈代谢，让肌肤更加明亮紧致。脸部护理安瓶不愧为我们美丽肌肤的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>至尊法宝<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"text7_em\" style=\"clear: both; line-height: 20px; text-indent: 24px;\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/a1.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"390\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/a2(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"654\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/a.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"696\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/b.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"652\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/c.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"731\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/d.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"532\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"text7_em\" style=\"clear: both; line-height: 20px; text-indent: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"text7_em\" style=\"clear: both; line-height: 20px; text-indent: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"text7_em\" style=\"clear: both; line-height: 20px; text-indent: 24px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red\">小贴士</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 黑体; color: red;\">：使用时，把安瓶滴在脸上，再用指腹轻轻涂开，并略加按摩至吸收。（在精华露、日霜、晚霜之前使用），使用安瓶时一定要仔细阅读说明书，以免因为使用方法错误而造成浪费或反效果。一支安瓶最好在<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>小时内用完。</span><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/a.jpg\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n</span></div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201306/thumb_img/278_thumb_G_1370716576313.jpg', 'images/201306/goods_img/278_G_1370716576512.jpg', 'images/201306/source_img/278_G_1370716576056.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '5', '1369456004', '2', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '1370717849', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_goods` ( `goods_id`, `cat_id`, `goods_sn`, `goods_name`, `goods_name_style`, `click_count`, `brand_id`, `provider_name`, `goods_number`, `goods_weight`, `market_price`, `shop_price`, `promote_price`, `promote_start_date`, `promote_end_date`, `warn_number`, `keywords`, `goods_brief`, `goods_desc`, `goods_thumb`, `goods_img`, `original_img`, `is_real`, `extension_code`, `is_on_sale`, `is_alone_sale`, `is_shipping`, `integral`, `add_time`, `sort_order`, `is_delete`, `is_best`, `is_new`, `is_hot`, `is_promote`, `bonus_type_id`, `last_update`, `goods_type`, `seller_note`, `give_integral`, `rank_integral`, `suppliers_id`, `is_check` ) VALUES  ('279', '8', 'MBB60', 'BB霜', '+', '51', '12', '', '9999', '30.000', '220.00', '220.00', '0.00', '0', '0', '200', '', '', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;font-weight:\r\nnormal\">完美<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜产品说明<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red\">产品名称：<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜 <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red\">代<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>号：<span lang=\"EN-US\">MBB60 <o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red\">规<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>格：<span lang=\"EN-US\">30ml <o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;color:red\">售<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>价：<span lang=\"EN-US\">220</span>元<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;\r\ncolor:red\">保 质 期：<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>个月</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\ncolor:#404040\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">B.B</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">霜是<span lang=\"EN-US\">Blemish Balm</span>的简称，<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜原来是对剥皮或美白（增白）后，受损和损伤的皮肤保护和修护使用的再生霜，因此对皮肤的问题给予及时迅速的改善，能够改善和弥补皮肤的缺点，因此而得名叫<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; BB</span>霜发展至今，经历了第一代<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜（伤痕保养霜），第二代（融合了保养品和粉底的双重身份），现在已经推出第三代<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜，科学技术不断的创新，将最初的<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜在脸上使用不透气，皮肤干燥甚至长期使用皮肤会长痘痘这种<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜与保养霜的概念相对矛盾，第三代<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜解决了<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;color:#404040\">三大问题：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#404040\">、新生肌肤通透性好；因为第三代<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜所用的最新美容科技分解的分子量更小，在用到脸上以后不会堵塞毛孔，透气性很好。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#404040\">、深层滋养：由于分子量小，可以直达皮肤的基底层，直接作用于细胞，有利于营养成分的吸收是第二代<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜的三到四倍。在这个基础上，完美的<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜，还添加了深层保湿的概念，在<span lang=\"EN-US\">BB</span>霜中添加保养成份和保湿最佳分子：小分子水在里面，利用最新尖端成分包埋技术可以更好的补充皮肤水分，使皮肤长期处于滋润状态，保湿性能好，长期使用皮肤不会干燥。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;color:#404040\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\ncolor:#404040\">、轻松卸妆，由于营养成分被吸收的完全，所用卸妆用一般的卸妆液，或者温水加洁面乳就可以了。（用洁肤啫哩和柔和洁肤乳就可以）。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">霜的使用重点：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、在肌肤做完基础保养后，上妆前直接擦上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，不能将粉底液混合成为万能化妆品，如此一来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">会失去对皮肤的再生功能。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">霜因使用天然性成分，因此阻断紫外线时间较短，建议使用前还是擦上抗紫外线的美白润肤隔离霜，才能有效抵抗紫外线。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">BB</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">霜虽然具有遮瑕覆盖的功效，但如果特殊情况下需要较浓厚的底妆，还是需要擦上粉底类产品，达到长效持妆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; BB</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">霜使用妙招：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; 1</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、使用之前一定要脱角质，否则妆容不会平整细腻。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 27pt; font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;\">2</span><span style=\"text-indent: 27pt; font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">、用之前先涂美白润肤隔离霜。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">、卸妆干净彻底。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 15.75pt; text-align: center;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:黑体;color:red\"><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/1(1).jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"1118\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/images/upload/Image/2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"1028\" alt=\"\" /></span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:黑体;color:red\"><br />\r\n</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 15.75pt; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 13.45pt 0cm; line-height: 15.75pt; text-align: center;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n黑体;color:red\">注意事项：本品可能对少数人体有过敏反应，如有不适，请立即停用。</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.5