span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">激活细胞活力，延缓皮肤衰老</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> A.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟中的异柠</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">檬酸钙等成分能扩张毛细血管，促进微循环，增进皮肤细胞的物质代谢，强化细</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">胞活力。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">B.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟所含的超氧化物歧化酶，过氧化酶，维生素</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">C</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，维生素</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">E</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，胡萝卜素等自由基清除剂，能清除引起细胞衰老的自由基，延缓皮肤细胞衰老。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">收敛，调和皮肤芦荟天生的收敛作用，能使皮肤坚实而细致，预防皮肤松弛、起皱；粘蛋白成分能调节皮肤的水分和油脂，使皮肤保持在平衡状态。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 3.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">滋养皮肤</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟中含有的糖类，氨基酸，维生素</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，矿物质，酵素，有机酸及水，是皮肤必需的营养素，芦荟中的这些成分分子小</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，渗透力强，可进入皮肤的内层。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 4.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">保护皮肤</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> A.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">实验证明，芦荟液能在皮肤细胞表层形</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">成一层皮肤膜，能有效的锁住水分；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">B.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟能吸收部分紫外线，有防晒作用；</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">C. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟有杀菌，消炎，中和微生物毒素的作用，有效的预防各种微生物引起的皮肤</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">病。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 使用方法：洗脸后，将芦荟胶与水按</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的比例</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">稀释后均匀的抹在脸上即可，每日</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">2-3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">次，日间不宜抹太厚，睡前可抹厚些（作</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">营养面膜）。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<h2><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n27.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\ninherit;mso-hansi-font-family:inherit;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">（二）黄褐斑，雀斑</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n27.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 黄褐斑也称肝斑，是发生于</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">面部的一种色素沉着性皮肤病。妇女妊娠，月经失调，盆腔疾病，外在</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">表现为前额，颧，鼻，上唇等处片状黄褐色或咖啡色斑，大小不一，边缘清</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">楚，表面光滑，无自觉症状。有时黄褐斑互相融合，形成蝴蝶状外观。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 雀斑的发生可能和遗传及曝晒日光有关。大多在</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> 6-7</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">岁开始出现，好发在面部，有时颈和手背等处也可发生，为针头至绿豆大小</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">黄褐或淡黑色斑点，成群或疏散分布，表面光滑，无自觉症状。夏季经强烈日晒</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">后，颜色加深，数目增多，冬季则颜色转淡，数目也减少。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 黄褐斑，雀斑有先天就易出现的人，但是经过紫</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">外线的辐射后，更易产生。化妆品过敏，精神紧张，偏食，肝脏，肾脏等内脏机</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">能低下等原因，使体内黑色素生成后沉着于体内，不能顺利排出，都可能是造成</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的原因。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 防晒和脱色是祛斑的关键，</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟胶有利于祛斑，这是因为：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟中含有芦荟素，蒽醌，肉桂酸酯等成分都</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">对部分紫外线有吸收作用，能隔绝部分日晒。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟胶中所含的氨基酸类，有机酸类，芦荟辛</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">等成分有抑制酪氨酸酶活性，阻碍黑色素形成的作用。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 3.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芦荟能增强微循环，促进细胞的新陈代谢，逐渐去除皮肤中沉着的色素。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 治疗方法：洗脸后，将芦荟胶与水按</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">的比例</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">稀释后均匀的抹到脸上，在有斑的部位多做按摩，以促进皮肤吸收，增强微循环</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">日</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">次，日间的</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">次不宜抹得太厚，而睡前的涂抹可厚一些。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> &nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 说明：祛斑至少需要三个月才会显效，因为皮肤</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">中沉着的色素要通过细胞的新陈代谢才能脱掉，要耐心坚持治疗，另外也需查明</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">病因，去除病根才能治愈。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<h2><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n27.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\ninherit;mso-hansi-font-family:inherit;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">（</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:27.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:inherit;mso-hansi-font-family:inherit;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">三）青春痘</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:27.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:red;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 概述：青春痘是一种常见于青年人的毛曩，皮脂腺的慢性炎症。有以下别称：痤疮、寻常痤疮、暗疮、酒刺、青春蕾、发蕾、发疙瘩、粉刺等。好发于青年男女面部和胸、背部。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> &nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 病因：目前认为由内分泌旺</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">盛引起。体内的雄性激素（男女体内都有雄性激素）水平相对增高，使皮脂腺发</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">育旺盛，分泌增多；同时雄性激素又使毛曩，皮脂腺导管角化，栓塞，导致又多</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">又浓的皮脂不能完全排泄出去，逐渐积聚在毛曩口，加上毛曩壁上脱落的上皮细</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">胞，这样浓稠的皮脂就与脱落的细胞混合在一起，成为干酪样物质栓塞在毛曩口</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">内，就形成了痤疮（白头粉刺）。疮疱顶端部分逐渐干燥，又经过空气的氧化作</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">用及尘土的污染而变色，便形成常见的黑头粉刺，由于粉刺的挤压和局部游离脂</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">肪酸的侵入，引起毛曩，皮脂腺的炎症反应，出现丘疹，脓疱，结节，脓肿及瘢</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">痕等各种表现。</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 方法：成熟的有脓包的豆豆，你可以用洗干净的手把脓包挤掉，然后再伤口上擦上芦荟胶，可以多用一点点。</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><b><span style=\"font-size: 24pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; color: red; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">（四）芦荟胶的美容用法</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶可以用来当面霜</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 当面霜的话用量不能太多，多按膜让皮肤充分吸</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: inherit, serif; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">收．如果用量太多，皮肤吸收不完，容易造成搓泥现象．因为芦荟多的时候可能有点粘的感觉．冬天擦了芦荟胶后保湿力度可能不够，会觉得不油腻，非常的清爽，用了非常舒服．</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">芦荟胶可以用来做面膜</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 有两种用法：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 18pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span styl